Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.21,0:00:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to just conclude, and then a few remarks about why addictive persons react the way they do to any threat to their addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see now, if happiness is something that lies outside of you, and if you've given the power over your life to that out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you can now see why you react the way you react to any threat to that, what you now believe to be the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's a relationship, that person might leave my life, the terror at that, I might lose my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see why people now react the way they react, and in knowing that, you know much better how to handle them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A person here, if you tell them they cannot drink anymore, if you put them in a hospital, if you pull them into treatment, will go into grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the mourning and the depression about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not because of the loss of alcohol for your life, it's because you're cut off from this state,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and the feeling that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.31,0:00:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, one will never more experience that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:01:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The state of apathy and hopelessness that almost led to suicide came out of the conviction that I am now and forever cut off from any access to this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not from alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,By that time, alcohol made me throw up, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Half an ounce of it had a violent and terrible negative effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hated it, and I detested it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't grief and mourning over the loss of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was grief and mourning for the same reason that the person...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in Lost Horizon is in grief and mourning over the loss of that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you go into fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Any threat to your supply, then, is not the fear of the loss of the drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the fear of the loss of this state, that you will have to live on this planet forever, the terror,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that you will never again experience a connection with that which is real, because it's their connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Another name for what's on top of the board is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is real again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You will always be in the plastic world of the solar plexus and the foreverness-chasing of the forms of all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The desiringness is obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's part and parcel of the entrapment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stand between a person and his source of supply, he may well kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it does happen, because you are cutting him off from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really what you are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,His experience of that which is his own godness, his own higher selfness,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,People will, of course, go into a rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So now you see the reactions to when we threaten a person's addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When you call him to question, when you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,George, don't you think you're drinking too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what you're bringing up in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what you're bringing up in him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All of his survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you're experiencing God too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really what you're saying to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're saying to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're implying now is a threat of his connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we get through talking today,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll see a much different way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of holding the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore how to approach the person,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so that they don't go into a panic over loss, or a rage,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,or end up hating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They will divorce you, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you threaten their supply,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll say, well, you and I are not getting along,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They will leave out of anger, out of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of the loss of their supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Any threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just wanted to clear that up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of why people react the way they do to the loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What the loss is that they're feeling threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the drug, and it's not the alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, after a while, a person doesn't care what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as it accesses this energy state.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the psychological explanations of addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,don't hold water clinically and experientially.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The psychological explanation is that they're running away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,from reality, that the person drinks because they
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,are trying to escape their fears, their anxieties,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,their angers, their resentments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:04:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorazine will get rid of your anxiety for a couple weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One good shot of Thorazine, and you won't feel nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,until probably Christmas time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Antidepressants will get rid of your depressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A combination of the two will get rid of your anxiety
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and your depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pharmacologically, I did that for 30 years as a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I got rid of people with psychopharmacology.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But nobody ever calls you for a refill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever says, Doc, my prescription
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for antidepressants and Thorazine went down the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,With Percodan, it always goes down the toilet, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My four-year-old daughter ate the prescription
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,for Percodan and got thrown out with her diapers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,because you gave me a repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody asked for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The elimination of these negatives
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is not what is sought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, these are born willingly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to access this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because as the addiction goes on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of these higher states
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes briefer and briefer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're followed by prolonged states of agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And the person is actually willing and will accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That this is going to bring them prolonged agony,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,even for a few moments of that experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And people will tell you when they come back into the program
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,who've been out,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it wasn't going to last more than a couple of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just had to, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Reconnect with that experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At whatever the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So it isn't the running away and people will say,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't drink to escape from life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I drank so that I could enjoy it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So that I could be more with life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't drink so I could avoid going to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I went so that I could go to the party
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and be more with life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,More with the party than I would have been
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,had I been in my normal state.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,See, that which is sought now begins to explain
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,really what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,These energy states are,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,these fields of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,as I said, are impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And they totally dominate how we experience life
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and how we experience the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So we did one column over here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,called Brain Chemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We can put columns all the way across the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're going to start marching across the board now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll put here the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How do these energy fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,see these energy fields are so powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that they literally have control
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,over what happens in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of what you're holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See the difficulty in people and consciousness work
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is to be able to grasp what is the power of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That it is so all powerful that they can't even get
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that it has power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field is so powerful that it literally
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,controls your perceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It controls the experiences that comes into your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You might look at this energy field as a grid,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,an energy grid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This grid then
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,creates and controls what goes in and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So that a person,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in this state of apathy, let us say,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,state of apathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,when they look at the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what do they literally see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a world do they experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They experience a world of hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even read that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be into apathy about my handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As you see, it is not hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's legible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, the energy field of apathy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,creates a perceptual field
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and an experiential
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,field in which what you see
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is hopelessness in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you look at is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You open the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It talks about an international situation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,with so-and-so, and you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,well, that's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It talks about world hunger, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hunger has always been with mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the mind will always find
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,intellectual rationalization to justify
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the position of the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This relationship is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister-in-law and her husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hopeless, that marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So you begin to see hopelessness everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And because you're holding hopelessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it brings into your life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think it's hopeless that you can train your dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, to do it outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you can be sure that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're holding that this dog is hopeless,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're never going to get him to the train
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,because you are holding a powerful energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that says he is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog is coming from a much less powerful energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and he will just go with your hopelessness
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and do it on the rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, from the most mundane
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to the most profoundly spiritual levels, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,our energy fields are dominated by that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,which we're holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Our relationships, you know, reflect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At this level down here of guilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we start going into the hells,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the hells going from there on down,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in which life seems to be an endless source of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, coming out of guilt, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,we have the world of pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,see, at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we have the world of hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless that the pain is going to be inevitable
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,because from this level,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,pain is part and parcel of all of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,all of experiences accompanied by pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The next higher levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a sad world, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The world of grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it is a sad world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the person in hopelessness walks down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and sees the hopelessness of society,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,hopelessness of civilization,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,hopelessness of man,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,hopelessness of man's condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This person, instead, sees sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in walking down the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the person sees the children
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and how sad that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing the pain that they're going to go through
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as they grow up, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The sadness, they look at the old people and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't that sad, the old people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was at a restaurant in Sedona
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,one time when that happened, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking at some people at the next table
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and they looked to me like they were in a state of bliss,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,they were all in a state of total oneness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they were so connected
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and had known each other for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and nothing needed to be said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,they just sat there blissed out with each other, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so happy to be in each other's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And the person with me said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,look at those old people, isn't that sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that sad? What was sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I couldn't see anything to be sad about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, the person was referring to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what they're projecting onto the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no sadness there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you open the paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,there is much, if you are into sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to be sad about, is that not so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There is much to be hopeless about,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,if that is where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing but sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are into a refueled of 30,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the world of pain is the world of sin,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you see page after page of sin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sin and wrong, being wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As you move up, you move into,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the sad world,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you move up into the fearful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the world of fearfulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of course, everybody is familiar with,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,from robbers, to muggers, to rapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to the IRS, to God knows what,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,what people think of you, people's opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you'll be well, help, wealth,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,all the endless fears,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and the enormous amount of human energy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that goes in to then defend themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,against these fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, a typical apartment in New York City
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,has six locks, and then it has
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,L-shaped crowbars around it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it has alarm systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it has bars in the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you go out, you may well get mugged,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is being held in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know people who have been mugged six times in a row,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and still living in the same high-rise apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been mugged six times in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And when are you moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how could I get a rent, you know, like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I get a rent like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, there's the self-reinforcement,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the self-reinforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it's fearful, the person has,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,an investment that this is a fearful world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,because the investment in this being a fearful world
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,then makes everything in their life meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If they weren't living in a world of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,if they couldn't put that investment into the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,then none of their life would make sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're busy preparing for old age,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,incurring themselves with insurance,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and locking their doors,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and double-locking their cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and their whole life is one prevention
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of the fearful happening in their life,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,which, of course, makes it manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the investment in fearfulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then the life suddenly has no meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your whole life about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like this person's investment is into
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a sad world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you try to take that away from them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,now what is the context of their life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Their whole life has been to prove
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is a sad place,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:12:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,where you lose everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,where loved ones turn against you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,where bosses don't appreciate you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,where those whom you invest with cheat on you, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Their whole investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's an investment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a secondary gain and a secondary payoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It merely reinforces it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really what sets the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as intention goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's certainly the secondary payoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In psychoanalysis that's called secondary payoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The secondary payoff reinforces the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see that which you set by your own intention
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,then sets the energy of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That field then determines what you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you see why people move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They move so slowly in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's almost a deadlock,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which you think the world is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,perceptually comes back to you as that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,which reinforces your belief
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that that's the way the world is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,which reinforces again
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that that's the kind of experiences that you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This person here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a frustrating world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The person into that solar plexus wanting this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,desiring this is never happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're endlessly critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They want everything to be different than the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The endless criticalness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the endless lack of satisfaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the desiringness, the wantingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we can see why making more millions
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,actually is not very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are dissatisfied,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,they're worth 50 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and that same dissatisfaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that wantingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,wow, I've got it made,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll go and be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and bliss out someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The same energy that earned the first 50 million
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,now drives them to earn more millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no end point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point at which the person can feel complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,satisfied, contented, happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,as we said,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,happiness is an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that begins at around 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what you get is satisfaction and pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say in this energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to get satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can plunge the dagger in your enemy's heart
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,oh there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels good at the moment that you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you get pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and you get satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But that will not hold you up tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person has to then go back in memory
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to the satisfaction
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and the person is then dependent on the memory
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of these past experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,because the present reality
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the source of their happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The awareness and consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of the truth of who they are
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and the present reality
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the source of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The person in frustration then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,desiring this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,as we said,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is seeking more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But because they're on this energy level,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,we said that all that the world offers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is about 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,all the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So 50 million will bring you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,a solar plexus,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,satisfaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and enjoyment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in which we calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of that is about 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you earn another 20 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you will still have
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,energy experience of 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So more and more sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,going to bed with more and more people,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,more and more status symbols,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,more and more money
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,leads people who feel like that eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,into suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and they become strange
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,when they get old
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and they end up in the tabloids
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,with long fingernails and weirdness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and no one can understand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,why with that many billions of dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,this person is not happy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and instead they're paranoid,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,totally isolated from life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and live a very wretched existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This eventually leads up to anger
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and so we get a world of conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We get the world of conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The angry person sees
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,life as many wars
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Down here at the bottom of the box
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is lose-lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At the bottom of the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At the middle of the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it's win-lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the box then,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,if I win, you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore relationships,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,business dealings,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,all transactions
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,are held in a win-lose
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,proposition in the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Down here, everybody loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go back to live with the family,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they all lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They're miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They lose their TV set.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lose-lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's automobile insurance gets canceled
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,after racking it up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's lose-lose for everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is win-lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And the angry person then sees
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,everything as conflict, competition
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and they have to guard against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's the chip on the shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,as one moves into pride and ownership.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,With pride goes, of course, ownership.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the world of status.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The world of status symbols.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See, this is all the same person
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,walking down the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See how differently,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean a different person
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,walking down the same street.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is seeing nothing but
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that which he hopes God will punish
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for its sinfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is seeing the hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at those newspapers on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're seeing hopelessness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This person is seeing the sadness of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This person is scared as hell
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,walking down the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a mugger or a raper
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,or somebody out to get him every second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course they spot him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an old friend of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,who used to be a mugger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,before he started teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's now dead, God bless him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Paul Steinberg,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,who was the national coordinator
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And Betty Martin used to talk a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And he used to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,as a mugger,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,they just knew who was muggable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They just stood in the doorway, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And the one that would walk by
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,furtively like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,they would instantly head for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They were very easy to knock over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So the fearful, like, pull it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull that which they fear to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So the world of status, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the person is walking down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and they see your Gucci shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they get your Neiman Marcus handbag,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they get your Saks Fifth Avenue sweater,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they get your so-and-so hairdo,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they get your so-and-so glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they get your, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is status.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They want you to get in your so-and-so car,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,hopefully not dented,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,hopefully this is yours model.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but a Cadillac is not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the Cadillacs,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I find out that there are various
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,gradations within Cadillac, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You find out about these things
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if you look into them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that all these things
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,have gradations of status
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,within them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought a Cadillac
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,was something fantastic,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but I found out it's
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,which Cadillac, not any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That attractiveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that seductiveness of things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,which we project onto it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,which doesn't exist
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,within the thing itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,which Madison Avenue capitalizes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See, when you smoke a cigarette,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't mean you're going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,riding across the horse
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,with a 10-gallon hat
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and looking like Mr. Seductress,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Movie Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It just means you're going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,smoking a cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You wear a certain perfume,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to smell good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean that all the men
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,are going to fall down
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,like dominoes, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this whole energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,this whole miasma,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,this charisma that is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,spun around purposely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the world of status, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is very much that world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of all what we have projected
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,onto things, symbols,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,because these things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,are all only symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of taking care of that lack
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,of inner self-esteem,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,which, if we had,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,all these things would be enjoyable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,only for what they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but not for what our fantasy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,adds onto them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,what does the world become like
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,at the level of courage, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What does the person
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,who is holding that energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,coming from that space,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,how do they experience
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the same street?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the world like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fascinating challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exciting, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a world of exciting opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,growth, challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,People in that space
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,will say,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I only got one life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,everything there is to experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what there is to learn here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,from my mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,from my mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to face them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,handle them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,cope with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to overcome this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, life is seen
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as an exciting,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the world is an exciting challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and the experience of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,then, is exhilarating.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a person in that energy level,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is excited to get up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and see what is the challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of this day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and the empowerment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:21:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,as you move up into neutral
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is a world of okayness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the world of okayness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a challenge anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if I get into college.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.08,0:22:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any resistance now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.08,0:22:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to how the world is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is seen as okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One is into neutral about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of a detachedness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,or it could be a non-detachedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.62,0:22:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To how the world is,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's a letting go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The benefit is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the release of a lot of energy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.68,0:22:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that was being held
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in resistance down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of that resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is let go of.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the downside
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of this energy field here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The upside is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The downside is flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, people say,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,would you like to come to the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if you go to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:22:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.00,0:23:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, very often you come across as flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there are people
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,who do a certain consciousness technique
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.06,0:23:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that they are not even aware of,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.06,0:23:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but it dumps them into neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of them are described
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.06,0:23:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,by other members of the community
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.06,0:23:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.06,0:23:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, these people are flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't invite them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.06,0:23:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't invite them
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.06,0:23:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because they are so flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The restaurants don't even like to see them
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.06,0:23:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.06,0:23:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they are so flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.06,0:23:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if they leave a tip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.06,0:23:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's okay if they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.06,0:23:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the waitresses don't like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The downside is egocentric flatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The upside is an okayness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and a willingness to go along with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, its upside is that willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to go along with life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.06,0:23:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,without resenting it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,without resisting it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,without getting depressed about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,without being angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,without being moralistic,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.06,0:23:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,without getting into right and wrong about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.06,0:23:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it is a move up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,towards acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, then we get,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.19,0:23:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,as we move into acceptance,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.19,0:23:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we move into a world of harmony,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.19,0:23:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,a world of easygoingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.19,0:24:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and we move into an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Competitiveness comes in about 180.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Cooperation comes in about 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as we move into acceptance,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.21,0:24:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,we move into a world of togetherness,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of not togetherness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.21,0:24:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,as Hollywood looks at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.67,0:24:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but a togetherness in which
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.67,0:24:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,things are included in,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.67,0:24:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,things are included in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Cooperation, then, means
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.92,0:24:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the respecting of the rights of others
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.92,0:24:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and the moving together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.92,0:24:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a person in this energy level
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.92,0:24:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,who has a used car lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.92,0:24:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,he hears that another used car lot
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.92,0:24:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is opening down the block,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.92,0:24:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,he goes into competition with that guy
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.92,0:24:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and feels that he's going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.92,0:24:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See, he lives in a world of win-lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.92,0:24:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, he only can see
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.92,0:24:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that he's going to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.92,0:24:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,by the other used car lot opening up
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,on the same block.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.92,0:24:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This person up here in cooperation
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.96,0:24:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,when he hears another used car lot
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.96,0:24:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is opening up on his block
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.96,0:24:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,says, fantastic,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.96,0:24:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that'll pull more used car buyers
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.96,0:25:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,from all over the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.96,0:25:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,will become, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.96,0:25:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the center for used cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.96,0:25:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe the two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.96,0:25:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,can get together and, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.96,0:25:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,advertise together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.96,0:25:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, he sees working with that guy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.96,0:25:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that you pull in more
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.96,0:25:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so that two used car lots
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.96,0:25:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,will now pull three times
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.96,0:25:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as much customers, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.96,0:25:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of twice as many.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.96,0:25:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he wants to join his energies
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.96,0:25:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,with someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.96,0:25:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so that everyone benefits
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.96,0:25:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because he's in to win
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.96,0:25:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and win-win.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.96,0:25:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this energy level then
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.96,0:25:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is called win-win.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.96,0:25:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I sell more used cars
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.96,0:25:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and so do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.96,0:25:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you advertise,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.28,0:25:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the better for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.28,0:25:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The more one art gallery advertises,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.63,0:25:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the better for all the art galleries.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.63,0:25:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's better for an art gallery
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.63,0:25:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,than to have four or five
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.63,0:25:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,in the same building
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.63,0:25:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,because it pulls all the art buyers
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.63,0:25:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,from surrounding communities
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.63,0:25:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,into the same building.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.63,0:25:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we move up to the god of,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.68,0:25:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we move up to the world of,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.75,0:25:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,we move up to the world of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.39,0:25:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened over here, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.39,0:25:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the process of one is one of revelation
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.39,0:26:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and the release of certain endorphins.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.39,0:26:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now the person begins to see
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.68,0:26:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and experience phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.84,0:26:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that people down here are not seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.84,0:26:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not seeing or experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.84,0:26:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the lovingness which is also there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.84,0:26:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This person may see the envy there,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.35,0:26:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but they don't see
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.35,0:26:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is also love there,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.35,0:26:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that although there is envy,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.35,0:26:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,there is also love.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.35,0:26:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The cancellation, the not seeing,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.64,0:26:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the unable to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.64,0:26:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the loveness that goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.64,0:26:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,between all human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.64,0:26:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This lovingness is going on
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.18,0:26:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,all the time between everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.18,0:26:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and every circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.18,0:26:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As this field opens up,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.98,0:26:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.98,0:26:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As you say hello to the doorman,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.98,0:26:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize that there is
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.98,0:26:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,an enormous lovingness going on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.98,0:26:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're loving the doorman,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.75,0:26:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,he's loving you,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.75,0:26:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and you become a part
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.75,0:26:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of his joy of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.75,0:26:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I used to live
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.75,0:27:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in New York City on Fifth Avenue,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.75,0:27:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a whole routine of doormen
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.75,0:27:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that I said good morning to.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.75,0:27:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you missed one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.75,0:27:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,they would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.75,0:27:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,where were you yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.84,0:27:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Something was missing from their life
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.84,0:27:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that was a touch of joy
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.84,0:27:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that that mutual greeting brought,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.84,0:27:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and I miss seeing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.84,0:27:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I miss seeing their happy face.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.32,0:27:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there is a lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.32,0:27:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that goes on all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.32,0:27:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in all circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.32,0:27:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's just not visible,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.32,0:27:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just not visible
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.32,0:27:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,until the energy field reaches that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.32,0:27:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you begin to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.32,0:27:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to see that
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.39,0:27:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,going on all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.68,0:27:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's true, there is this,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.68,0:27:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is also that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.68,0:27:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.68,0:27:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Down here it's either or,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.68,0:27:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and this begins to include in
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.68,0:27:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you see the lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.68,0:27:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that is going on all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.68,0:27:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to see the response of nature
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.68,0:27:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to your own consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.68,0:27:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to become aware
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.41,0:28:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that that which is growing around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.41,0:28:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.41,0:28:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are vibrating out
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.41,0:28:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is affecting all of life around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.41,0:28:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,all of life around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.41,0:28:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I once killed a plant with consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.15,0:28:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was once a plant that I hated,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.15,0:28:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't like what it stood for.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.15,0:28:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't like what I remembered because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.15,0:28:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't like what it was doing in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.15,0:28:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just consciously hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.15,0:28:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And in about eight weeks it was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.15,0:28:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor little plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.15,0:28:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the plant I ever killed, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.15,0:28:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, St. Peter, I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.01,0:28:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.01,0:28:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ cursed the fig tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.43,0:28:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.43,0:28:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy that we radiate out then
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.28,0:28:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,affects all of life around us,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.28,0:28:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,affects all of the life around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.28,0:28:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we move up to this level here,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.28,0:28:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we begin to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.28,0:28:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you cannot read that, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.28,0:28:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.28,0:29:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What becomes revealed to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.36,0:29:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because this is called revelation,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.36,0:29:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,is the incredible beauty of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.49,0:29:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,As you move towards the top of the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.49,0:29:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it's incredible perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.97,0:29:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not aesthetic beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.97,0:29:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Aesthetic beauty is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.97,0:29:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aesthetic beauty is a prettiness, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.23,0:29:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.58,0:29:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're now moving out of the world of perception
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.58,0:29:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,into the world of knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.58,0:29:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the inner experience of the incredible essence of all things
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.58,0:29:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,as they express themselves through their perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.58,0:29:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This came to me one day as I was sitting at home
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.64,0:29:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the kitty was sitting there on the rug.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.64,0:29:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I looked at the kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.64,0:29:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly, I got...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.64,0:29:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the kitty is sitting there
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.64,0:29:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,as an absolute perfect expression of its kittiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.73,0:29:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.73,0:29:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The kitty sits there and it is itself
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.80,0:29:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,perfectly, absolutely,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.92,0:29:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in the incredible beauty of its isness being what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.92,0:30:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And you begin to see that everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.92,0:30:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody has those experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.12,0:30:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody in the audience, I'm sure, has had those experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.12,0:30:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll come when you're walking through the woods
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.56,0:30:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and suddenly there's that inner silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.56,0:30:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a hushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.56,0:30:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell when it's going to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.56,0:30:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,because all of a sudden everything becomes hushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.56,0:30:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it slows down
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.60,0:30:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's always to me like a slow motion movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.60,0:30:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden the incredible,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.60,0:30:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,magnificent,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.60,0:30:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,perfection and beauty of all things
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.60,0:30:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and you are one with that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.60,0:30:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and you are not different than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.60,0:30:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That that is what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.60,0:30:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see the truth of all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.60,0:30:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,God is all that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.78,0:30:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So that incredible perfection, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.78,0:30:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And now how do you see people?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.78,0:30:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the rose as it is half unfolded,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.88,0:30:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,see, it's unfolding its perfection
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.88,0:30:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and absolute perfectness.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.88,0:30:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The incredible beauty, the harmony,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.88,0:30:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,its expression of that which it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.83,0:31:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the unfoldingness of that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.83,0:31:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is perfect in its unfoldingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.83,0:31:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you look at another human being,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.83,0:31:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you look at someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.83,0:31:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see the incredible beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.83,0:31:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and it radiates out from their inner self
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.83,0:31:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,almost like a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.83,0:31:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the incredible beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.83,0:31:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of the unfoldingness of that which they are
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.83,0:31:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,as they are coming into the awareness, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.99,0:31:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Stealing is no longer really good in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.99,0:31:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, that's the lesson I'm getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.99,0:31:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the lesson is,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.24,0:31:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,booze and drugs are driving me
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.24,0:31:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,into insanity and self-destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.24,0:31:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever that lesson is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.20,0:31:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So those are the perceptual worlds, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.91,0:31:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The world being holographic, a hologram.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.91,0:31:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you all know what a hologram is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.07,0:31:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a three-dimensional representation
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.07,0:31:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's done by the interface
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.07,0:31:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of a laser light which is aligned photons
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.23,0:32:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and normal light bouncing off an object
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.39,0:32:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and creating a photographic plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.39,0:32:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you take a fragment of that photographic plate,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.32,0:32:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and you run a laser beam through it again,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.32,0:32:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it recreates the whole,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.32,0:32:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and it recreates the whole spatially
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.32,0:32:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in space, three-dimensionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.36,0:32:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is connected with everything else
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.36,0:32:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,because every person and everything
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.43,0:32:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is off a vibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.43,0:32:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, these vibrations all interface, do they not?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.43,0:32:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you give off a vibration
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.52,0:32:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and you give off a vibration,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.52,0:32:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,then the two must intersect somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.59,0:32:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, all things are connected
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.59,0:32:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,with all other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.62,0:32:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is separate from anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.62,0:32:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the holographic dimension,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.91,0:32:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the title of several very popular books.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.91,0:32:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So this hologram then,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.77,0:32:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the world then, as we see it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.77,0:32:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,from the description of these various,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.77,0:32:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,these are really portholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.87,0:33:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,These are perceptual portholes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.87,0:33:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in which we project out
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.00,0:33:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that which we are holding
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.00,0:33:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and then experience back our own projection
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.00,0:33:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and say, see, isn't it so?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.86,0:33:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So the world then, the street that we were talking about before,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.86,0:33:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is like a hologram.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.86,0:33:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And starting at the bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.63,0:33:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so as you walk around this hologram,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.76,0:33:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,it goes from all the same hologram.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.95,0:33:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All depends on where you're looking at it from, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.95,0:33:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.01,0:33:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But looked at from here, it's pain and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.48,0:33:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look at the pain and suffering, isn't that terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.48,0:33:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And the person literally re-experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.48,0:33:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,this pain and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.48,0:33:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They literally see it on the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.48,0:33:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They hear it in the voice, in the sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.48,0:33:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in the vibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.48,0:33:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The person in this energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.41,0:33:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,then gets back that energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.41,0:33:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and they experience that as what is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.41,0:33:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as the person up here is entranced.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.48,0:34:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, they look at the old people
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.48,0:34:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and it almost makes you weep.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.48,0:34:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at them and you see the incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.48,0:34:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,state of peace and joy that they are into,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.86,0:34:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and inner peace and joy
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.86,0:34:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in the divine presence of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.44,0:34:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the world of perception,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.20,0:34:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the hologram of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.20,0:34:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So how if we see how one experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.16,0:34:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the world that way, then how does one,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.16,0:34:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll extend that to God, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.16,0:34:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll see something of significance perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.98,0:34:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So how does God come out then
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.98,0:34:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.91,0:34:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At the bottom of the box then,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.91,0:34:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that apathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.91,0:34:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.20,0:34:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we can say that God is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.20,0:34:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who believes in death
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.83,0:34:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and absolute destruction,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.83,0:34:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,then God is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.18,0:34:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So one can become a great philosopher.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.18,0:35:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If one has a high IQ,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.18,0:35:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is that the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.40,0:35:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then tends to justify
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.40,0:35:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,one's inner position.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.40,0:35:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect comes to the service
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.40,0:35:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and tries to make explainable and acceptable
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.40,0:35:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that the essence of human life is nausea,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.01,0:35:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that man is hopeless,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.01,0:35:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and that God is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.33,0:35:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can become quite popular for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.33,0:35:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Selling books that God is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.32,0:35:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,God doesn't really care about all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.32,0:35:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So the books go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.32,0:35:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So all you're really telling,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.32,0:35:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,what are you telling the world then
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.32,0:35:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,when you write a book about God is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.32,0:35:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're telling the world
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.32,0:35:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is your own inner spiritual position
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.32,0:35:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of hopelessness and apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.32,0:35:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.32,0:35:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to that person,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.32,0:35:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no experience of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.32,0:35:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.32,0:35:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,God is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.32,0:35:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To them,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.32,0:35:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,God is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.32,0:35:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind being so powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.32,0:35:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if it holds that God is dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.96,0:35:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,then I can assure you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.96,0:35:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,God will be dead to that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.96,0:36:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,God will be dead to the person
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.03,0:36:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,who holds that God is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.03,0:36:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be no experience of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.03,0:36:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,outside of one's own personal ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.03,0:36:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So through one's own inner experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.03,0:36:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,one can say,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.03,0:36:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never experienced anything
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.03,0:36:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,other than that which is in the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.67,0:36:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of therefore concluding
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.12,0:36:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a very limited person,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.12,0:36:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and not through conscience,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.12,0:36:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,instead the person projects that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.12,0:36:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and says God is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.12,0:36:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As we get up higher then,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.98,0:36:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we get to the conceptualizations
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.98,0:36:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of the God of the worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.98,0:36:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The sinner you see is a worm,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.98,0:36:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I being a hopeless sinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.40,0:36:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are people who hold that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.46,0:36:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,there may be a God,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.46,0:36:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but he would not want anything
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.46,0:36:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.46,0:36:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And many of those people indulge
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.10,0:36:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in all kinds of self-flagellative activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.10,0:36:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.10,0:36:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the pursuit of suffering then
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.48,0:36:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as an assuagement for guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.48,0:36:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and the hope that one will reach God,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.48,0:36:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,indulging in an energy field of 30
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.92,0:36:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,ad infinitum
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.92,0:37:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,will not get you to the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.92,0:37:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.92,0:37:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore the futility
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.92,0:37:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of wallowing in guilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.92,0:37:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and penance,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.92,0:37:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and sinfulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.92,0:37:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and guiltness,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.92,0:37:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because it takes you exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.92,0:37:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to the opposite end of the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.92,0:37:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,God is not experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.92,0:37:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in an energy field of 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.92,0:37:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As you move up into grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.11,0:37:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the God who doesn't want anything
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.11,0:37:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to do with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.11,0:37:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,those are the people
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.11,0:37:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,who are abandoned by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.11,0:37:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandoned by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.36,0:37:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I called out to God
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.07,0:37:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and there was no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.07,0:37:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandoned and separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.07,0:37:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandoned and separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.55,0:37:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move up to fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.55,0:37:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,then you move into levels
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.55,0:37:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,where God is the great punisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.55,0:37:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,God is what you are terrified of.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.55,0:37:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,God who is the avenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.19,0:37:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The avenger, the punisher,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.73,0:38:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,he really becomes the persecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.44,0:38:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He really becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.79,0:38:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is demonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.38,0:38:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The angry person,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.38,0:38:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the fearful person,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.38,0:38:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the person who is full
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.38,0:38:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of sinfulness then,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.38,0:38:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,can only conceive of a God
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.38,0:38:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,who is the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.80,0:38:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the demonic gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.80,0:38:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In this way of holding God,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.80,0:38:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,he is capricious,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.80,0:38:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,willful,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.28,0:38:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,he is fitful,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.28,0:38:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and then God took pity
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.28,0:38:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,on the people of something or other
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.28,0:38:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and decided not to demolish their city.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.28,0:38:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This God is also jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.44,0:38:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.44,0:38:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's jealous and he's paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.44,0:38:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's capricious, he's fitful,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.44,0:38:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's the ultimate in destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.69,0:38:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He is not only out to destroy man
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.69,0:38:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and his civilization,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.69,0:38:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,he's out to destroy your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.69,0:38:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So for one sinful thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.62,0:38:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,he will throw you into hell forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.62,0:39:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't leave much room for the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.48,0:39:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What would the devil do
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.48,0:39:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with this kind of a God around?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.48,0:39:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His job has been taken away totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.48,0:39:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you fear
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.48,0:39:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,next to a God like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.48,0:39:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst has already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.48,0:39:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.48,0:39:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really the God,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.48,0:39:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the demonic God of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.87,0:39:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important because
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.87,0:39:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the next energy level is one of pride
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.87,0:39:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and this demonic conceptualization
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.87,0:39:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of God is what often leads
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.12,0:39:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to the next level.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.32,0:39:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,On the level of pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.32,0:39:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got two positions possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.76,0:39:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of one's intuitive perception,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.76,0:39:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,inner awareness of truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.76,0:39:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,one throws this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.76,0:39:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And you may take then on one side
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.76,0:39:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the position of the atheist
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.76,0:39:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,or the agnostic
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.76,0:39:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,who comes from the pridefulness
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.30,0:39:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of the intellect unknowingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.30,0:39:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks that's all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.40,0:39:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks at the demonic conceptualizations
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.40,0:39:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of God and says,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.40,0:39:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that God isn't even as good as my aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.40,0:39:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My aunt is a more loving being than that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.40,0:39:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and throws out
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.40,0:40:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the demonic conceptualizations of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.40,0:40:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And then concludes having done so
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.46,0:40:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that he has thrown out God.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.46,0:40:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the error.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.65,0:40:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mixing the map with the territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.65,0:40:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He confuses the map with the territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.78,0:40:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Having found an error in the map,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.78,0:40:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he throws that out thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.78,0:40:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he's now destroyed the territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.78,0:40:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Throwing out the baby with the bathwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.58,0:40:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Having thrown out,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.58,0:40:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,what has he thrown out?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.58,0:40:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's thrown out concepts.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.58,0:40:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But a concept is not the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.58,0:40:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A concept is a symbol for the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.58,0:40:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And in this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.64,0:40:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a distorted concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.64,0:40:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So he throws out the distorted concept
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.64,0:40:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and now he has thrown out the thing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.64,0:40:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That he has handled the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.87,0:40:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So the agnostic says,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.87,0:40:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't take a position about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.87,0:40:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.87,0:40:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.87,0:40:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.87,0:40:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No proof one way or the other is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.87,0:40:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking that the intellect
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.87,0:40:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is the sum total of human experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.87,0:40:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect alone and unaided
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.87,0:40:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot prove the existence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.87,0:40:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,or disprove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.87,0:41:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other side of this field would be
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.41,0:41:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the person who takes the opposite position.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.41,0:41:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That my knowledge of the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.48,0:41:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is the only truth there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.48,0:41:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore you are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.48,0:41:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have the endless religious wars
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.48,0:41:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and bigotries.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.48,0:41:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That go on from my position
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.92,0:41:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and my way of seeing it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.92,0:41:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is the only truth and the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.92,0:41:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So the arrogance,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.92,0:41:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the contempt,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.92,0:41:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,see the denial of the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.92,0:41:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth is possible for anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.92,0:41:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The contempt for their spiritual positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.92,0:41:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The defensiveness about one's own spiritual position.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.92,0:41:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore the endless angry
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.92,0:41:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,confronts and endless religious wars and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.92,0:41:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That go on on this energy level of pridefulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.92,0:41:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens when we get to the level of courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.63,0:41:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because so far we've been below the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.63,0:41:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens when you get to the level of courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.72,0:41:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You start running into the God of AA.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.72,0:41:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.72,0:42:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,God of AA.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.72,0:42:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You start running into the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.72,0:42:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first time now you're above the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.72,0:42:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.72,0:42:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is you don't know anything about God, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.95,0:42:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is you have a lot of hearsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.46,0:42:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Written by very authoritative and impressive people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.46,0:42:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming from authoritative sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.46,0:42:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is your own inner knowledge and experience of the truth of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.46,0:42:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's zilch.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.46,0:42:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.46,0:42:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in AA they talk about the God of your own understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.46,0:42:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The God of your own inner experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.46,0:42:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth that has come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.46,0:42:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the truth that has come to some saint 2,000 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.46,0:42:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,on the other side of the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.46,0:42:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,walking on the road to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.20,0:42:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're walking down the street and your knees go to water
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.20,0:42:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and you need a drink or you need a fix
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.20,0:42:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened to somebody else a couple thousand years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.20,0:42:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is not going to come to your aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.20,0:42:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What you've realized, the experience of that which is present within you now
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.20,0:42:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you need right this second.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.45,0:43:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When the desire to drink or take a drug hits you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.45,0:43:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to have something that is right here, right now
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.45,0:43:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and rock-like connected within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.45,0:43:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That services you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.45,0:43:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's experienced within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.45,0:43:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.45,0:43:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.93,0:43:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That is for you what is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.93,0:43:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you have the God of eminence
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.93,0:43:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, in theological terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.96,0:43:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The God of transcendence is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.96,0:43:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The God of transcendence is not of much use.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.96,0:43:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The God of transcendence is what everybody tried in religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.96,0:43:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And people in AA, including the priesthood that's there
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.96,0:43:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,will say the God of religion I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.96,0:43:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.96,0:43:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The God who is out there was of no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.96,0:43:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to come into AA
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.96,0:43:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to find the inner experience of the reality of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.96,0:43:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The God that is within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.96,0:43:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The God that in theological terms
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.96,0:43:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is the God that was imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.96,0:43:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is within myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.38,0:43:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the God of AA.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.38,0:43:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,God as you understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.38,0:43:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's understood in AA
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.38,0:44:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that as you grow, as you transcend in the box
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.38,0:44:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,your experience of God will then
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.38,0:44:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,parallel that inner growth
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.38,0:44:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and your experiences will be commensurate with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.38,0:44:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You then move up, as we say, to a God of mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.80,0:44:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the God of unforgivingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.80,0:44:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the God of forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.80,0:44:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the God of love
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.80,0:44:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.68,0:44:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,AA says
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.68,0:44:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it acknowledges only one authority
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.84,0:44:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is a loving God.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.12,0:44:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And they mean by that a loving God expressed
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.83,0:44:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,through your own individual experience
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.83,0:44:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and through the group consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.83,0:44:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the conscience of the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.83,0:44:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And so people learn to rely on sponsorship
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.83,0:44:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because they ask
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.83,0:44:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that through that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.05,0:44:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the will of God be known in their own personal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.05,0:44:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And they begin to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.05,0:44:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that that energy field which is coming through the group
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.47,0:45:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is that expression of God
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.47,0:45:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,as it comes into their life
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.47,0:45:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in the group experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.04,0:45:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The God of love, the God of mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.04,0:45:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We start moving up into the God of oneness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.04,0:45:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The God of oneness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.04,0:45:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We start moving into that God of perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.04,0:45:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally as we get near the box
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.04,0:45:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the top of the box
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.04,0:45:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we move into the experience of the presence itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.20,0:45:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience of the presence itself
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.20,0:45:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,which is often called illumination.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.20,0:45:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Those states described by the saints
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.20,0:45:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,usually associated with sainthood.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.10,0:45:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The total overwhelming experience
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.10,0:45:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of the divine presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.10,0:45:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ineffable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.56,0:45:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.56,0:45:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Transforming.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.56,0:45:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a few moments of that experience
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.56,0:45:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,transforms one's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.76,0:45:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the experience of Bill Wilson of course
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.76,0:45:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,when Bill surrendered.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.04,0:45:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In that moment he asked
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.04,0:46:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is there a God?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.04,0:46:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And if there is, I asked him
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.04,0:46:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked to experience him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.11,0:46:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And in one instant the room lit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.11,0:46:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And he felt the infinite presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.11,0:46:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of that moment
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.46,0:46:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that second
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.46,0:46:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,all of AA was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.46,0:46:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the transformation that has occurred
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.46,0:46:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in social consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.46,0:46:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole self-help group movement
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.46,0:46:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of America
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.46,0:46:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,of which AA was the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.91,0:46:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They now run into the hundreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.91,0:46:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no human ailment or dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.91,0:46:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That there now is not some place
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.91,0:46:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can go
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.91,0:46:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and experience human understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.91,0:46:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and help from that absolute authority
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.91,0:46:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes from only having lived that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.91,0:46:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.91,0:46:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,See, having lived it yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.91,0:46:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,gives you the power of healing that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.91,0:46:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,which you have healed within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.91,0:46:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That whole awareness of that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.07,0:46:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,came out of that one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.07,0:46:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What a powerful moment that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.07,0:46:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That moment transformed
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.10,0:46:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,all of therapy in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.10,0:46:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Transformed the whole mental health movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.10,0:47:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Took us out of hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.26,0:47:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, in the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.55,0:47:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it was just alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.55,0:47:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The condition of alcoholism
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.41,0:47:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,was a hopeless condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.41,0:47:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.41,0:47:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no cure for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.41,0:47:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no help for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.41,0:47:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Interestingly, out of Carl Jung
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.60,0:47:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it was Carl Jung's integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.60,0:47:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and honesty
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.34,0:47:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that accounted for the birth of AA.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.34,0:47:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when Roland saw Carl Jung
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.34,0:47:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and thought he was cured
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.44,0:47:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and then he went back to the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.44,0:47:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and he fell back into this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.44,0:47:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He went back to Carl Jung
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.01,0:47:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and Carl said,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.20,0:47:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alas, but my science, my art cannot help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.20,0:47:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But there have been times
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.20,0:47:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in the history of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.20,0:47:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,where people with this affliction
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.20,0:47:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,have thrown themselves into a spiritual group.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.20,0:47:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And there have been reported throughout man's history
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.24,0:47:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,isolated cases
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.24,0:47:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in which out of this experience
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.24,0:47:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a recovery has been possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.24,0:47:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I myself offer you no hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.24,0:47:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And so Roland went back to the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.24,0:48:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in a state of hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.24,0:48:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Total hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.24,0:48:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But he followed Carl's advice
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.49,0:48:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and he went to the Oxford Groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.49,0:48:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Oxford Groups being based on
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.49,0:48:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,basically the 12 steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.49,0:48:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A shortened version of the 12 steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.49,0:48:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was out of that hopelessness then
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.97,0:48:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that Roland surrendered.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.97,0:48:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of his surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.97,0:48:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,he achieved sobriety
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.97,0:48:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and then passed it on through Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.97,0:48:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.61,0:48:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the great power then
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.61,0:48:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.61,0:48:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The space that allows for grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.61,0:48:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The great power of grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.06,0:48:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In just the moment that Bill
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.06,0:48:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,experienced that experience
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.06,0:48:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,all of what came forth
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.06,0:48:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it's as though he
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.06,0:48:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in opening himself to that power
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.06,0:48:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of God within him
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.06,0:48:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like he opened a window for the God energy
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.06,0:48:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to flow into the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.06,0:48:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And from that experience then
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.06,0:48:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,all of AA and all of it was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.06,0:48:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The enormous transforming power
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.06,0:49:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of such moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.35,0:49:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a child I experienced some of these states.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.35,0:49:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And in teenage
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.35,0:49:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a paper route one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.35,0:49:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in northern Wisconsin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.35,0:49:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was 20 below zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.96,0:49:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A terrible blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.96,0:49:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And to get out of the cold wind
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.96,0:49:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a hole in a snow bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.02,0:49:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I sat in the snow bank
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.02,0:49:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to get out of the blizzard
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.92,0:49:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,an incredible state came on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.92,0:49:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of infinite peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.92,0:49:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible. Indescribable.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.92,0:49:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No one was touched by
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.92,0:49:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,God himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.84,0:49:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And all that I was was
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.84,0:49:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,replaced with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.13,0:49:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And this incredible infinite state.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.13,0:49:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which was personal
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.13,0:49:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,David no longer was
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.13,0:49:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.16,0:49:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And so those states
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.16,0:49:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,come into everyone's life
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.19,0:49:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,briefly or
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.25,0:49:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in this case unsought.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.25,0:49:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was no context in which to hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.25,0:49:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no context
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.38,0:50:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in which this 14 year old
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.38,0:50:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,could hold that experience
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.38,0:50:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,meaningfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.05,0:50:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it returned in
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.53,0:50:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,January 1965
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.53,0:50:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,again
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.79,0:50:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,there was no pre-existing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.79,0:50:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,context in which to hold
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.79,0:50:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.79,0:50:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of the infinite omniscience
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.36,0:50:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and omnipresence.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.36,0:50:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And that lasted for about a year
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.75,0:50:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,in that period.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.91,0:50:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And then in January 1981
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.91,0:50:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,again that state came on
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.97,0:50:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,running up in the numbers in the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.97,0:50:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.45,0:50:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And so having personally gone up and down
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.45,0:50:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole scale
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.45,0:50:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of those experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.45,0:50:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and then
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.77,0:50:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of that with
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.77,0:50:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the desire to create
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.41,0:50:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the context
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.89,0:50:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to create a way in which to hold all that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.89,0:50:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so that all can be purified
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.89,0:50:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,within the way that you're holding it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.89,0:50:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so that it becomes a permanent
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.89,0:51:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.56,0:51:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So that those people who've had those experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.56,0:51:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,come out of it with that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.56,0:51:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.60,0:51:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,With kinesiology we'll
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.63,0:51:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,just test the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.63,0:51:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of some of these experiences especially
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.63,0:51:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the essential
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.82,0:51:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,point that I'm trying to make
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.82,0:51:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is what one is addicted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.82,0:51:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.85,0:51:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are addicted to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.85,0:51:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is that you seek
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.98,0:51:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,by addicted to I mean that desire
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.98,0:51:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to return to that experience
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.98,0:51:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the overwhelming desire to return
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.98,0:51:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to that experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.98,0:51:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've experienced the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.98,0:51:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there is nothing that this world has to offer
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.98,0:51:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.98,0:51:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It dissolves into a space
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.98,0:51:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,through it that you move through
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.98,0:51:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to return to that experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.98,0:51:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All of life then becomes transformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.98,0:51:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all held within a different context.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.98,0:51:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And so
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.40,0:51:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd do some kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.40,0:51:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How many here have never experienced kinesiology?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.40,0:52:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a third of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.61,0:52:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Kinesiology is very
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.61,0:52:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,simple in that what you're testing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.61,0:52:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is energy and energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.61,0:52:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as it expresses itself in
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.61,0:52:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,particular power.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.77,0:52:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How about if I get a subject
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.77,0:52:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a willing subject from the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.77,0:52:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I may want to be the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.77,0:52:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's seen kinesiology before?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.77,0:52:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come up and just be the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.77,0:52:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,person that I demonstrated with?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.52,0:52:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What kinesiology is testing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.56,0:52:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is the integrity of an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.56,0:52:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,as it expresses itself
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.56,0:52:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in the harmony and balance of
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.56,0:52:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the acupuncture system.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.56,0:52:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The acupuncture system
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.56,0:52:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,running down twelve meridians is everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.56,0:52:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in California
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.56,0:52:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,generally sophisticated about such matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.56,0:52:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Running down the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.75,0:52:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,twelve meridians, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.45,0:52:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.48,0:52:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,see the minute you go above the line
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.48,0:52:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,when you go above the line you instantly
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.68,0:52:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,go strong. When you go below
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.68,0:53:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the line you instantly go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.68,0:53:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a very neat way to test
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.68,0:53:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth of anything by
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.68,0:53:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,asking for the integrity of the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.68,0:53:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,field. What you're testing is the integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.68,0:53:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of an energy field. But
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.68,0:53:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,what we'll do today is demonstrate the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.68,0:53:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of some of the things we've been saying with kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.68,0:53:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we do is we ask
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.68,0:53:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the subject and we're going to do this as a class.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.68,0:53:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll become ones and twos.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.68,0:53:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One becomes the tester, one the testee.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.68,0:53:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important to experience the truth of this
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.68,0:53:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because otherwise you'll just hold it in intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.68,0:53:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you experience the truth of what we're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.68,0:53:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it really changes your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.68,0:53:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you do is you raise
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.80,0:53:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,your left arm, the person is being tested
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.80,0:53:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have them look at the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.80,0:53:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look straight ahead at the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.80,0:53:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and don't smile at the person because
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.80,0:53:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,if you smile at them you're radiating out an energy
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.80,0:53:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,field up in here and you're affecting
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.80,0:53:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the response. So you try to be
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.80,0:53:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,detached, clinically detached
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.80,0:53:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and have them look at the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.80,0:53:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and then when I press down you resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.80,0:53:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.99,0:53:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you can let her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.99,0:53:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When you test, you test with two fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.99,0:54:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you're testing is for a general feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.99,0:54:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,of the person's muscular strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.99,0:54:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not trying to break their arm and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.99,0:54:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You know. You're just trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.99,0:54:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,get a feeling for their power, for their energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.99,0:54:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You press down with two fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.99,0:54:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Two fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.20,0:54:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When you do that, I'm going to ask him to hold
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.20,0:54:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,something in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.97,0:54:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I want you to hold in mind somebody you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.97,0:54:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,like or somebody you've experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.97,0:54:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,unpleasantly or something in your life
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.97,0:54:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that's not so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.24,0:54:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that is something that is below the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.24,0:54:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody he fears, somebody he hates,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.24,0:54:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,an experience that is unpleasant,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.24,0:54:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a regret, a grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.24,0:54:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now I'd like you to hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.78,0:54:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,someone you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.29,0:54:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be your kitty, it could be your dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.29,0:54:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it could be Jesus, it could be your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.29,0:54:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.40,0:54:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.09,0:55:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is above the line, the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.09,0:55:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,love being that
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.09,0:55:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,not different than that which is the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.09,0:55:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,empowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.09,0:55:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is a lie weakens.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.09,0:55:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And the integrity of the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.09,0:55:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,fuel can be tested out instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.09,0:55:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It has widespread
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.32,0:55:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,applications once it begins to dawn on
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.32,0:55:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you that you can get the truth of
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.32,0:55:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,things that are beyond your personal opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.32,0:55:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you read
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.38,0:55:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a book, before you wander in the metaphysical
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.38,0:55:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,shop and decide that
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.38,0:55:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Swami so-and-so is going to be your savior,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.38,0:55:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very neat to test out
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.38,0:55:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,what his integrity field is and what his intention
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.38,0:55:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is and the space that he's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.44,0:55:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,from. So you'll find
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.89,0:55:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that it has very important
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.89,0:55:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,clinical applications and we'll
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.89,0:55:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,experience some of them today.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.89,0:55:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's divide up into ones and
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.08,0:55:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,twos and we're going to test out three or four
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.08,0:55:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,propositions and
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.08,0:55:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,then at the end you can ask a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.08,0:55:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,question and get an answer to that which you've
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.08,0:55:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,always wanted to know the truth of.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.08,0:55:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And get a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.92,0:56:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,reasonable assurance that you're
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.92,0:56:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,getting the truth. So why don't we just
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.92,0:56:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,divide up into ones and twos
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.92,0:56:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of us stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.04,0:56:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Number one is going to be the tester,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.04,0:56:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,number two is going to be the testee,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.04,0:56:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,then we'll switch. Number two will
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.04,0:56:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,become the testor, number one
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.04,0:56:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the testee.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.55,0:56:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So here's what I'd like you to do is
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.55,0:56:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to not say anything. This can all be done
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.55,0:56:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in silence. If you just listen to me it'll go
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.55,0:56:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,very fast and it'll be quite a rewarding
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.55,0:56:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,experience. Just decide who's number
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.55,0:56:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,one. Number one put up your hand so we
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.55,0:56:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,know who's your number one. Okay, you are the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.55,0:56:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And number two is the testee.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.55,0:56:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So the first thing I'd like you to do
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.55,0:56:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is just to ask them to hold out their
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.55,0:56:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,arm and test
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.55,0:56:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,their arm just like I did with him
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.55,0:56:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,with two fingers. And don't forget
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.09,0:56:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not trying to break his arm, their arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.09,0:56:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just trying to get a feel for their power
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.09,0:56:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and their strength. Try to be detached
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.28,0:56:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and impersonal as though it was
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.28,0:56:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,a clinical research.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.28,0:56:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So you look
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.28,0:56:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at the wall and just
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.28,0:57:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,ask them to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.57,0:57:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When they're ready, have them resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.57,0:57:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you get a feeling for their power and their energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.57,0:57:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? Got it? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.21,0:57:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everybody then, the first thing I'd like
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.21,0:57:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you to do, those who are being tested, is hold
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.21,0:57:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in mind or picture or
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.21,0:57:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,remember something or someone
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.21,0:57:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that's unpleasant in some regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.21,0:57:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Some loss that you've experienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.21,0:57:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,an accident, something coming up in the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.21,0:57:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,future that you wish you didn't have to face,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.21,0:57:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,a ticket you got for
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.79,0:57:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,something. If all fails
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.36,0:57:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,picture yourself tied to a railroad track in the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.36,0:57:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,train is bearing down and getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.36,0:57:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone you don't like
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.62,0:57:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,from the past. Someone you don't like
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.62,0:57:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in your present life. Somebody you fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.62,0:57:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody who scares you, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.77,0:57:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody who really scares you when you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.77,0:57:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,come up against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.22,0:57:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Has everybody got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.35,0:57:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'd like you to hold something
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.35,0:57:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,or someone that you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.86,0:58:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, it could be your kitty, it could be your
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.86,0:58:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,dog, it could be your mom, lover, girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.86,0:58:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,mom, dad. You can change
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.36,0:58:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,arms if you want. First get acquainted with the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.36,0:58:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,power of that arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.36,0:58:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say, don't push so hard you wear them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.36,0:58:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,With two fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.40,0:58:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you can get a feeling. They're either weak or they're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.40,0:58:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.40,0:58:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's got to be somebody you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.91,0:58:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Some value that you cherish.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.91,0:58:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Some space that is very
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.91,0:58:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,sacred to you. Anything that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.94,0:58:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.58,0:58:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.08,0:58:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,experience, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.20,0:58:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The next thing I want to test out is a proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.20,0:58:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So get ready to be tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.20,0:58:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give you the proposition. I want you to hold this
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.20,0:58:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,proposition in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.96,0:58:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when you have got the proposition in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.96,0:58:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,nod your head so that the person can
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.96,0:58:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,press down and test you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.96,0:59:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The proposition is that the drugs have the power
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.96,0:59:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to get you high.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.38,0:59:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The power is in the drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.38,0:59:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's drugs that get me high.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.64,0:59:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's drugs that have the power to create
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.64,0:59:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that experience within
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.19,0:59:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,either myself or those who are addicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.19,0:59:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.36,0:59:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an alternate proposition
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.36,0:59:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can get ready to be tested
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.36,0:59:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and hold this concept in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.70,0:59:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that the drugs remove the obstruction
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.70,0:59:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to the experience of that which I am
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.70,0:59:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and allow me to experience the bliss
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.70,0:59:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is my own higher self.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.34,0:59:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The drugs block the not-self
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.34,0:59:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and allow me to get closer to
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.34,0:59:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of my own inner self.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.60,0:59:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The power comes from my own inner
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.60,0:59:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,godness.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.17,0:59:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the source of the power
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.46,1:00:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of that experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.30,1:00:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the next thing is you're going to ask
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.30,1:00:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.07,1:00:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything you always really want to know
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.07,1:00:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the answer to.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.32,1:00:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have an addictive problem
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.32,1:00:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have a question in your mind
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.32,1:00:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you can say,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.32,1:00:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really addicted?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.32,1:00:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really an alcoholic?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.60,1:00:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.60,1:00:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask any question you want
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.69,1:00:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and then just indicate to the tester
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.69,1:00:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as it's answerable by yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.24,1:00:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to share this question
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.24,1:00:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you can just keep it in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.16,1:00:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything you really want to know,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.16,1:00:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,ask either that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.20,1:00:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the boss planning to fire me?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.58,1:00:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I really see a doctor about that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.08,1:00:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatchamacallit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.08,1:01:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you really want to know, ask about.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.08,1:01:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Does my mother really love me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.63,1:01:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.41,1:01:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my kitty really pregnant?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.41,1:01:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, any kind of question you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.41,1:01:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really pregnant?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.89,1:01:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now we'll switch.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.82,1:01:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll switch and again
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.82,1:01:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're silent I'll just guide you
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.40,1:01:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,through it and we'll do it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.40,1:01:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,First test the strength of the person
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.40,1:01:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so you get a feel for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.40,1:01:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just use two fingers.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.68,1:01:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the person resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.22,1:01:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist with all your strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.22,1:01:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, got that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.99,1:01:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The next thing you hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.99,1:01:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is someone you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.99,1:01:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.99,1:01:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Something painful.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.18,1:01:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Painful memory from the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.69,1:02:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you wish hadn't happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.69,1:02:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you fear might happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.69,1:02:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody who blows your mind
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.59,1:02:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,when you see them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.59,1:02:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.12,1:02:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold the devil back there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.36,1:02:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, now in contrast
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.36,1:02:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,just hold in mind the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.36,1:02:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the memory of someone you love.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.71,1:02:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Their image, their thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.03,1:02:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A memory of being with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.03,1:02:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound of their voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.24,1:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What they feel like to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.63,1:02:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What they look like to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.86,1:02:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it and test that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.86,1:02:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really dramatic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.86,1:02:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it is so definite.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.86,1:02:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.86,1:02:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.68,1:02:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.68,1:02:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, the next thing because we're
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.68,1:02:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,into the consciousness about addictions.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.68,1:02:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to hold in mind, get ready to be tested
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.68,1:03:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and then hold this concept in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.68,1:03:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the drugs that have the power
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.77,1:03:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to get me high.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.22,1:03:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience of bliss comes from the drug.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.22,1:03:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Drugs have the power to create that experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.76,1:03:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Test the truth of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.31,1:03:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now hold the contrasting proposition in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.31,1:03:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to be tested on this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.31,1:03:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That the drugs block off
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.31,1:03:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.34,1:03:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of my lower self and allow me
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.34,1:03:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to experience the energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.34,1:03:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or get close to the energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.34,1:03:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is my higher self.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.52,1:03:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience in consciousness that comes about
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.52,1:03:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,from the use of drugs
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.93,1:03:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,from intoxication
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.93,1:03:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is literally the experience
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.93,1:04:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,of my own inner presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.79,1:04:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And now everybody gets a secret question.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.79,1:04:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Or questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.11,1:04:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret question.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.43,1:04:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.43,1:04:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's face the truth of the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.60,1:04:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer you get now, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.60,1:04:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is the way it is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.60,1:04:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not set in cement.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.89,1:04:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you get an answer that you don't like,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.89,1:04:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,realize it's not set in cement.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.21,1:04:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That you have the power to transform
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.21,1:04:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that entire relationship
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.21,1:04:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,or situation
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.21,1:04:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and transform it within your life
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.21,1:04:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you can get a retest sometime later
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.21,1:04:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,holding it from a different space
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.21,1:04:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and get a different answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.21,1:04:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is the way you're holding it now
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.21,1:05:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way it's going to come out.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.66,1:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you're holding it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.11,1:05:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's sort of a fun experience, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.11,1:05:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A way of
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.13,1:05:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,ascertaining the integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.13,1:05:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of an energy field.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.13,1:05:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're testing is the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.23,1:05:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you hold something or someone in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.23,1:05:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you're asking what is the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.23,1:05:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,integrity of this person's intention
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.23,1:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or energy field in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.26,1:05:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Generally, the experience
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.26,1:05:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that I get when I work with families
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.26,1:05:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is the same as we do with the addicts.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.26,1:05:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,With the people who have become addicted
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.26,1:05:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we've been doing it for a couple of years
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.26,1:05:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,at the villa and the answers have always
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.26,1:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,been the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.25,1:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When we ask, does the drug have the power
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.25,1:05:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to create the experience
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.25,1:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,within yourself, they all go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.25,1:05:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we say
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.34,1:05:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is the truth that the drug
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.34,1:05:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,blocks that which you are not
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.34,1:05:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can experience
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.34,1:05:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or at least get into the ballpark
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.34,1:06:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of the experience of the truth of your
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.34,1:06:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,inner godness, they all go strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.34,1:06:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So at least within the addict population
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.34,1:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the one I've had the experience with
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.34,1:06:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it's been verifiable right across the board.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.34,1:06:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It is obvious
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.98,1:06:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,as you listen to
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.17,1:06:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,what we're saying today
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.17,1:06:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that no chemical has the power
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.17,1:06:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to create a 600 experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.17,1:06:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the energy fields
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.30,1:06:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of some of the things in our daily life
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.30,1:06:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and our daily experience
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.30,1:06:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and what can we learn from that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.30,1:06:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and how can we use that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.30,1:06:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in a way that's beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.33,1:06:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we end up holding
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.33,1:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,this information in such a way that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.33,1:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,healing comes out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.33,1:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That being the purpose of the communication.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.33,1:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We notice that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.00,1:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the science and medicine
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.00,1:06:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that which pertains
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.00,1:06:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to the mind, to the intellect
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.00,1:06:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to the mind with a small m
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.16,1:06:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that which pertains to the intellect
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.16,1:06:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and calibrates in an energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.20,1:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of about 425.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.20,1:06:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See that's the difficulty of the atheist
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.20,1:07:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,or the agnostic.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.20,1:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming from an energy field of the intellect
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.20,1:07:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,which is 425
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.20,1:07:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,how can you have any experience
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.23,1:07:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is outside the domain
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.23,1:07:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of the intellect and calibrates
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.23,1:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,at 600 and up.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.26,1:07:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is 425 cannot experience
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.26,1:07:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is 600 and up.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.26,1:07:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At 450
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.68,1:07:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,we run into that
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.68,1:07:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,which we call harmony.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.68,1:07:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.68,1:07:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So competition is 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.74,1:07:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We say competition
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.74,1:07:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is 180
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.74,1:07:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and cooperation
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.74,1:07:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is about 450.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.09,1:07:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually cooperation runs about 480.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.09,1:07:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Harmony,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.12,1:07:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,comparison as they move through
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.12,1:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,education
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.46,1:07:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.46,1:07:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,moves up through into that which is harmonious
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.46,1:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is cooperative
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.65,1:07:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and at 475
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.65,1:07:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,we see is the calibration
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.65,1:07:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.65,1:07:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In AA they talk about
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.65,1:08:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,we share our experience, our strength
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.65,1:08:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and our hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.75,1:08:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the energy fields that are being
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.75,1:08:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,shared?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.75,1:08:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Our experience of having gone through this whole experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.75,1:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.88,1:08:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The inspiration that comes out of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.88,1:08:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Our experience, our strength
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.04,1:08:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and our hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.13,1:08:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And strength being over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.52,1:08:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As you move up into
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.03,1:08:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,these heart levels then
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.03,1:08:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,at about 530
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.03,1:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we have simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.03,1:08:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In which the complexities of life
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.03,1:08:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,are now experienced because of one's
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.03,1:08:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,inner values
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.03,1:08:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're held in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.03,1:08:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're held in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.03,1:08:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And at 540 you have gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.12,1:08:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know 12 step groups
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.12,1:08:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,talk a great deal about gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.12,1:08:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gratitude to the program.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.12,1:08:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gratitude to Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.12,1:08:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gratitude
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.02,1:08:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,gratitude for their sobriety.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.02,1:08:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Gratitude to the grace of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.21,1:08:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore the gratitude itself
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.21,1:09:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because this is the same
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.21,1:09:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,energy level as healing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.40,1:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Healing and AA and gratitude
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.40,1:09:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,all come out about the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.40,1:09:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is grateful
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.40,1:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is healing
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.40,1:09:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and AA all come out about
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.44,1:09:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the same. So gratitude then
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.44,1:09:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is really a way of self healing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.50,1:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To be able to hold a thing
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.50,1:09:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,from gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.56,1:09:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you begin to see then how
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.56,1:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,some of the things in the lower part of the box
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.56,1:09:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,can be healed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.56,1:09:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They can be healed
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.56,1:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,from the way in which they are held.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.72,1:09:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,From the way in which
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.72,1:09:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,they are held.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.72,1:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So we said that worldly success
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.72,1:09:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,was about 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.72,1:09:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean you should throw out
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.72,1:09:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,worldly success at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.72,1:09:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What it means is
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.72,1:09:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,one can be grateful for that worldly success.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.72,1:09:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If one can say
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.84,1:09:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you God
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.45,1:09:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,for this enormous abundance.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.45,1:09:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For the enormous opening I have
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.80,1:09:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to utilize
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.80,1:10:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I have power over
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.80,1:10:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to communicate that which is helpful to the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.80,1:10:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.18,1:10:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to hold from love then
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.18,1:10:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,one's sexual opportunities
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.18,1:10:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,one's power in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.18,1:10:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,one's status. All these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.18,1:10:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the way you hold them
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.18,1:10:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to transform them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.18,1:10:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you hold your own past.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.18,1:10:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.28,1:10:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,as painful as it was
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.28,1:10:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I could not have learned that lesson
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.28,1:10:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,without having experienced it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.60,1:10:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was possible for me to learn that
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.60,1:10:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,some other way I would have.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.60,1:10:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously because I experienced it out
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.60,1:10:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,for me it was necessary
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.60,1:10:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to move from this space to that space
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.60,1:10:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to have lived it out
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.60,1:10:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and experienced it through.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.30,1:10:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So it opens then
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.30,1:10:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,an awareness of how we can begin
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.30,1:10:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to hold things
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.30,1:10:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so that they become healing
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.30,1:10:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so that they become sacred
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.30,1:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because of our touch
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.30,1:10:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the touch of how we are holding them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.10,1:11:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And at 570 then
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.10,1:11:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you become aware
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.10,1:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of that inner beauty
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.10,1:11:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the incredible beauty
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.10,1:11:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.13,1:11:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that beauty
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.13,1:11:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and its perfection
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.47,1:11:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the incredible beauty
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.47,1:11:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we see that the source of it
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.47,1:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is that which is sacred.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.47,1:11:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The sacredness of all of creation
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.47,1:11:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is the sacredness of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.47,1:11:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The incredible beauty
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.47,1:11:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of its expression
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.47,1:11:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and its absolute perfection
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.47,1:11:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as one gets near the top of the box.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.01,1:11:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of that
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.01,1:11:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that experience
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.01,1:11:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,then comes compassion.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.33,1:11:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The importance of these three things
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.71,1:11:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of courage
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.71,1:11:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of love
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.71,1:11:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and of compassion
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.71,1:11:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,because those are points of decision
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.71,1:11:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,which you can access
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.71,1:11:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the higher states of consciousness yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.71,1:11:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,To face the truth about things
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.51,1:11:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,even though it may be painful.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.51,1:12:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your commitment to lovingness
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.51,1:12:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,as the way you wish to be
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.51,1:12:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,as the experience
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.51,1:12:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of how you want to experience your life
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.51,1:12:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and how you value it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.51,1:12:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the lovingness for your own life
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.89,1:12:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and that of others
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.89,1:12:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and the development of compassion
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.89,1:12:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the revelation
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.89,1:12:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the release
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.15,1:12:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,then on the physical plane
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.15,1:12:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the endorphins
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.76,1:12:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the opening into the understanding of the human heart
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.76,1:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to clear up something else
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.20,1:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that came up during the break
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.27,1:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that release of the endorphins
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.27,1:12:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming from one's spiritual position.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.27,1:12:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important to realize
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.27,1:12:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that the body
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.27,1:12:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that goes on with it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.27,1:12:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming out of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.27,1:12:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It is life that creates the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.27,1:12:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It is one's spiritual position
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.27,1:12:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it is that commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.27,1:12:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and the exercise of that lovingness
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.27,1:12:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,which releases the endorphins
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.27,1:12:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it is not the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.27,1:12:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't, in other words
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.59,1:12:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,take endorphins and find yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.59,1:13:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in a high spiritual state.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.48,1:13:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a confusion of causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.48,1:13:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This world being the world
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.48,1:13:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,a manifest world of the expression
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.48,1:13:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which you are holding.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.48,1:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is not linear
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.80,1:13:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it is not as though there are two different levels
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.80,1:13:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it is not as though
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.80,1:13:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,what is being held in mind is now
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.80,1:13:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,cause and what is being expressed
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.80,1:13:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world is effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.80,1:13:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Although in a certain way
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.80,1:13:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of holding it that would be so.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.44,1:13:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually they both go on
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.44,1:13:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,simultaneously cause being
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.44,1:13:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,outside of the field of both.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.05,1:13:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause is outside the field of both.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.05,1:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is cause
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.15,1:13:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,creates both its representation
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.15,1:13:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in the manifest world
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.15,1:13:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way it is held in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.15,1:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.68,1:13:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I get going on causality
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.68,1:13:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a whole other trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.68,1:13:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But that compassion then
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.51,1:13:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is that desire
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.83,1:14:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that ability
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.83,1:14:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that dedication
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.83,1:14:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.83,1:14:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To understand the heart
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.83,1:14:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and as you see it's
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.83,1:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,way beyond condemnation
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.89,1:14:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it is beyond right and wrong
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.89,1:14:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it is an understanding
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.89,1:14:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of the nature and the essence
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.89,1:14:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.53,1:14:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And just at that level then
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.53,1:14:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,at 600
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.63,1:14:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,comes about things that we call wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.63,1:14:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.63,1:14:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,intrinsic to a person at that level
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.63,1:14:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is an inner gentleness.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.63,1:14:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And with gentleness
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.72,1:14:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,goes strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.95,1:14:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is the most powerful
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.95,1:14:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,in the universe
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.95,1:14:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is the most gentle.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.14,1:14:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And as that experience comes into you
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.14,1:14:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the thing that totally
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.14,1:14:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,wipes you out
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.14,1:14:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is its profound gentleness.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.14,1:14:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so exquisite
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.14,1:14:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,as that awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.14,1:14:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,dawns on you
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.46,1:15:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's almost
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.13,1:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,insufferable to experience it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.13,1:15:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the response
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.29,1:15:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of the remaining ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.80,1:15:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.80,1:15:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as you become aware of the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.96,1:15:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it disappears
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.96,1:15:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as the presence becomes all it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.96,1:15:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the beginning
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.96,1:15:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there is that feeling of awe
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.96,1:15:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and the incredible nature
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.05,1:15:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of that exquisite gentleness.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.05,1:15:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Also
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.88,1:15:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,its incredible power.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.88,1:15:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not only exquisitely
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.88,1:15:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,gentle beyond description
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.88,1:15:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but its power
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.88,1:15:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is indescribable.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.78,1:15:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Its power is
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.78,1:15:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,absolute and therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.78,1:15:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience is curiously
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.78,1:15:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,one of this
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.29,1:15:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,exquisite gentleness
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.09,1:15:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence of infinite power
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.09,1:15:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and at the same time
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.16,1:15:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it is rock-like.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.56,1:15:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never read that in any place but
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.56,1:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a rock-like
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.56,1:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,nature to the quality
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.56,1:16:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is exquisitely
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.56,1:16:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,gentle and also
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.56,1:16:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,all-powerful and
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.56,1:16:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.92,1:16:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that level
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.95,1:16:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,comes that which we have
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.14,1:16:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,at the top of the board
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.17,1:16:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is beyond all
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.17,1:16:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the peace of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.97,1:16:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And as that state approaches
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.74,1:16:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the intrinsic innocence
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.74,1:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with all things
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.00,1:16:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,which is part and results
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.00,1:16:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in compassion.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.19,1:16:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Exquisite awareness that within
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.19,1:16:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that the essence of all things
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.28,1:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in its perfection
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.28,1:16:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is that absolute innocence.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.28,1:16:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you see
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.63,1:16:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that innocence?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.63,1:16:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though the mind
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.19,1:16:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is like a computer.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.19,1:16:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though the mind
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.96,1:16:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.05,1:17:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens to the mind
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.05,1:17:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of the child? The mind of the child
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.05,1:17:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is in a state of innocence.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.05,1:17:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what happens
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.18,1:17:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind of the child
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.18,1:17:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is like the hardware you might say
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.18,1:17:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the programs of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.18,1:17:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,come in like the software
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.18,1:17:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin to program it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.63,1:17:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And what makes the child programmable?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.63,1:17:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes the child
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.66,1:17:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,programmable?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.85,1:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it not its intrinsic innocence?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.85,1:17:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you love your mother
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.62,1:17:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that whatever she says
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.16,1:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you incorporate as your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.28,1:17:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you love your dad
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.28,1:17:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,because you love your country
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.28,1:17:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you love your teacher
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.28,1:17:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,because you hold them in respect and honor them
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.28,1:17:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why you believe what they say.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.28,1:17:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the love of your peers
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.28,1:17:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and wanting to be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.28,1:17:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of your love for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.89,1:17:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So that intrinsic innocence
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.04,1:17:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,which is there
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.04,1:17:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,never changes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.52,1:17:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The hardware of the computer
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.52,1:18:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,never changes no matter what software
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.52,1:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,floppy disk you put in, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.52,1:18:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is the computer itself
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.52,1:18:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,never loses its innocence.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.52,1:18:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You just can hear different programs
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.52,1:18:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,put in a different program.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.61,1:18:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And so
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.76,1:18:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the awareness of the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.76,1:18:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of that within
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.69,1:18:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because it never leaves you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.92,1:18:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what's listening to my voice
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.84,1:18:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,right now, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.26,1:18:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it not your own intrinsic innocence?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.26,1:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That is listening
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.29,1:18:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is very second.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.28,1:18:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Understanding, listening,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.76,1:18:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,believing, incorporating
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.79,1:18:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in faith and trust
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.79,1:18:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that that which is being spoken is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.20,1:18:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you disbelieve it
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.71,1:18:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,then you reject it
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.71,1:18:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,from some opposing program.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.18,1:19:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And where did you get the opposing program?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.18,1:19:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You bought that out of your innocence, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.08,1:19:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you disagree violently
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.08,1:19:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with what I say
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.08,1:19:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,what's disagreeing with that is a program.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.08,1:19:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your own innocence you bought.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.08,1:19:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So your innocence is unsullied
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.08,1:19:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you agree, whether you disagree.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.08,1:19:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.14,1:19:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth of that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.14,1:19:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is totally unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.24,1:19:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth of that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.24,1:19:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is unchanged by the experiences
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.24,1:19:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that go through consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.24,1:19:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore the realization
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.65,1:19:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that that is its nature
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.65,1:19:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that that is the nature of what you are
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.65,1:19:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of what we all are
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.19,1:19:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of what we all are
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.19,1:19:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is totally unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.51,1:19:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It is exactly that which we have always been
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.51,1:19:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and always will be
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.51,1:19:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that that innocence is
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.76,1:19:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,unassailable
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.02,1:19:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and not be defended.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.53,1:19:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.80,1:20:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The undoing of all that it is not
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.80,1:20:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,allows one to experience
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.80,1:20:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth of that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.80,1:20:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the purpose
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.73,1:20:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of all spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.73,1:20:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is the removal of that which we are not.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.73,1:20:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is the removal
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.83,1:20:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of the clouds from the sky
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.83,1:20:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we can experience the sun
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.83,1:20:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,always shining.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.24,1:20:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In the proposition we were testing
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.24,1:20:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,with kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.24,1:20:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what we were really asking was
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.40,1:20:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,does the removal of the clouds
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.40,1:20:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,cause the sun to shine?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.26,1:20:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the removal of the clouds
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.26,1:20:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,cause the sun to shine?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.55,1:20:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is the sun always shining
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.55,1:20:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and when we remove the clouds
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.55,1:20:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we are aware that it is always there?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.55,1:20:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really comparably
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.55,1:20:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the metaphor of what we were asking.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.55,1:20:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The seeing of this
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.75,1:20:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,entire way of holding clouds
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.75,1:20:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and things then
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.75,1:20:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,reveals to us
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.75,1:20:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and after this lecture
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.75,1:21:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,things will begin to unfold
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.94,1:21:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,because the mind is always looking
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.94,1:21:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there is that within us
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.94,1:21:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,which is self-healing.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.94,1:21:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It is always looking for that
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.94,1:21:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,means, those tools
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.94,1:21:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the ways of healing ourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.94,1:21:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it begins to dawn on us
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.94,1:21:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that there are ways now
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.94,1:21:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of holding things
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.04,1:21:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that will bring about a healing
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.26,1:21:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that will come out of merely the way
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.26,1:21:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of holding it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.63,1:21:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The healing of many of these things then
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.63,1:21:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you are holding
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.13,1:21:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,from the lovingness
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.13,1:21:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,from the truth of that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.13,1:21:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you are not
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.13,1:21:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but you are holding it
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.13,1:21:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,from that which is greater
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.13,1:21:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than from that which is lesser.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.26,1:21:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When we are identifying with
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.26,1:21:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is lesser
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.26,1:21:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't look at it
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.26,1:21:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because we think I am that
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.26,1:21:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the false identification
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.26,1:21:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,with the small self.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.26,1:22:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot look at that within myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.00,1:22:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If our motivation
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.00,1:22:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if our intention is
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.00,1:22:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the healing within ourself
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.00,1:22:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and when we do it within ourself
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.00,1:22:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we do it within everyone
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.64,1:22:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,because we are the world
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.89,1:22:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,we are everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.89,1:22:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole implication
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.88,1:22:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of the holographic conceptualization
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.92,1:22:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it reveals
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.92,1:22:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are everyone
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.92,1:22:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that your consciousness is all that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.92,1:22:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So as we heal
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.92,1:22:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that within ourself
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.92,1:22:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,we heal it within the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.01,1:22:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people get into a conflict
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.01,1:22:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,about myself
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.01,1:22:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and or the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.88,1:22:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is myself is not different
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.88,1:22:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,than that which is the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.29,1:22:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heal it within myself
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.29,1:22:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,then I heal it for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.29,1:22:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As each of us heals these things within ourself
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.29,1:22:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,we raise the consciousness of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.29,1:22:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone benefits.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.29,1:22:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we heal ourself
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.29,1:22:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a win-win situation
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.29,1:23:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,because out of that lovingness
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.29,1:23:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to perfect the awareness of that
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.29,1:23:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,which we are
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.58,1:23:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,then comes the power.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.58,1:23:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Empowerment.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.58,1:23:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So the intention coming from this level
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.58,1:23:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,empowers the person
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.58,1:23:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to heal that within oneself
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.58,1:23:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,which needs to be healed.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.93,1:23:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming out of the way
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.93,1:23:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's being looked at.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.93,1:23:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming out of the way it's being held.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.96,1:23:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of that we begin to see
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.96,1:23:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that whatever we were
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.02,1:23:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in the past was necessary
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.02,1:23:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for us at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.12,1:23:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It is out of the desire
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.92,1:23:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for happiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.92,1:23:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It is out of the love of life
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.92,1:23:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that all of it came. Did it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.62,1:23:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say, angriness.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.62,1:23:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the angriness coming out of?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.62,1:23:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the angriness coming out of?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.00,1:23:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The angriness
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.13,1:23:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming out of your love for life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.13,1:23:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it not? And the thought
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.13,1:23:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that someone is going to impair it in some way.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.13,1:23:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So the way to get out of the guilt
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.13,1:24:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,about that
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.13,1:24:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is to look and see that underlying it all
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.13,1:24:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is that innocent,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.13,1:24:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,naive love for life
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.13,1:24:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the thought that
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.13,1:24:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,this is blocking my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.13,1:24:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All the negative feelings
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.20,1:24:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,are coming out of the thought
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.20,1:24:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that my happiness is out there
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.20,1:24:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and something is interfering with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.22,1:24:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I always say, and I don't know whether it's true or not
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.22,1:24:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I invite everybody to dial this in
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.22,1:24:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and test their kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.22,1:24:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can't really love unless you've hated.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.22,1:24:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't care enough
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.22,1:24:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,about life to hate somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.22,1:24:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,who you feel is threatening life itself
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.22,1:24:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,then you will never rise
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.22,1:24:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to the level of loving it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.22,1:24:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're in apathy
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.22,1:24:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't care enough about life
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.22,1:24:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't even get angry, would you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.22,1:24:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.22,1:24:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so sad that you can't even get involved in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.22,1:24:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitty Genovese or whatever it was
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.22,1:24:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,people just withdrew from the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.22,1:24:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't the commitment of life
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.22,1:24:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,enough to even be angry about it
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.22,1:24:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to even do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.22,1:24:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody went into apathy.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.22,1:25:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you look back
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.72,1:25:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,at the things that you condemn within yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.72,1:25:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you heal it, as you say
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.72,1:25:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in the becoming awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.43,1:25:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which I am
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.43,1:25:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,it was necessary for me to experience that then.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.43,1:25:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But at that time
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.75,1:25:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what I needed.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.75,1:25:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, that's what had to be with me
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.75,1:25:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because who I was at the time
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.75,1:25:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,thought that that was the best thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.75,1:25:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And doesn't the mind in its innocence
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.75,1:25:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,always choose
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.75,1:25:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that which it thinks is the best thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.75,1:25:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Does your mind ever do anything else?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.84,1:25:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It always chooses what it thinks at the moment
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.84,1:25:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is the best decision, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.84,1:25:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it gets into an impulse
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.94,1:25:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that it hates itself for later
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.94,1:25:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it still makes the decision
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.94,1:25:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that for me at this time
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.94,1:25:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the best thing to do is to throw the brick
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.94,1:25:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,through the son of a bitch's window.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.94,1:25:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Later I may feel guilty about that
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.94,1:25:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but at that moment the feeling
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.94,1:25:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that I must express my aliveness
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.94,1:25:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in that form that is meaningful to me
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.94,1:25:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,may well be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.07,1:26:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget the first time
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.58,1:26:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I met a guy coming in
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.58,1:26:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the parking lot
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.58,1:26:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was always a very
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.58,1:26:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess what you call people pleaser, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.58,1:26:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we got into conflict
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.58,1:26:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,about who had the driveway
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.58,1:26:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and so I gave him the finger.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.58,1:26:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'll tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.58,1:26:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was ecstatically happy. I had never done that before
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.58,1:26:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in my life. I never told somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.58,1:26:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to go you know where. Never did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.58,1:26:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fifty something
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.58,1:26:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,years old before I finally did that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.58,1:26:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was so pleased with myself
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.58,1:26:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you see, that I'd gotten up to that
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.58,1:26:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, not out of hopelessness
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.58,1:26:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,not out of fear
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.58,1:26:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,not out of fear that you won't be a
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.58,1:26:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual person if you do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.58,1:26:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be a spiritual person man
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.58,1:26:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,if you tell somebody where to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.58,1:26:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I got such a, I got hysterical
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.58,1:26:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,laughing over it you know. First I told him where to go
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.58,1:26:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I broke down and I almost went off the
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.58,1:26:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,road laughing at the whole thing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.58,1:26:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,because it was such fun. And then I went
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.58,1:26:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,around doing that a little while because I was getting off on it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.58,1:26:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and then finally gave up on it but
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.58,1:26:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it was really fun to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.58,1:27:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know where to go. You can go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.58,1:27:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, here, look. It was really
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.58,1:27:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,great fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.00,1:27:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Necessary, necessary to know that I
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.00,1:27:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,could do that. Necessary that I could hold
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.00,1:27:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it that way. That I could
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.00,1:27:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,experience it in a self-healing way.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.00,1:27:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See? And not go into guilt
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.00,1:27:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,about it and self-condemnation.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.00,1:27:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that which we've been
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.54,1:27:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,was necessary in the evolution of
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.54,1:27:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,our becoming that which we are
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.54,1:27:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming aware of. All of that
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.54,1:27:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is necessary. For the
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.76,1:27:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,addicted person then, in
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.76,1:27:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the interest of his own consciousness growth
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.76,1:27:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it is absolutely essential
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.76,1:27:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and it is absolutely necessary
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.76,1:27:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in this lifetime, at this time
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.76,1:27:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that this be what
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.76,1:27:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the person is experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.76,1:27:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely critical to their
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.76,1:27:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,life. That confrontation
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.83,1:27:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,with the absoluteness
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.83,1:27:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of facing the truth about yourself or
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.83,1:27:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,dying. And that's what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.83,1:27:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it takes a lot of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.83,1:27:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it took me. It was in the
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.83,1:27:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,teeth of death itself
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.83,1:27:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that the transformation took place.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.83,1:28:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It took all of it. It took all of it
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.83,1:28:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring about that surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.83,1:28:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And some people
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.79,1:28:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,know the ego is not so strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.79,1:28:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't take that severity, that
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.79,1:28:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,degree. In the old days in the
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.79,1:28:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,AA, it was thought that everybody had to reach
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.79,1:28:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the pits of hell before they
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.79,1:28:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,gave up. And of course we know
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.79,1:28:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that is not true.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.79,1:28:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not at all true that anybody
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.85,1:28:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,can learn from this education.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.85,1:28:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And from the education, from
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.85,1:28:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,this awareness itself, it raises the
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.85,1:28:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,bottom so that people don't have to go
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.85,1:28:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to this level called destruction
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.85,1:28:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,before they finally surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.85,1:28:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we've got time for
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.20,1:28:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a few minutes for questions and answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.20,1:28:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anything that you want to
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.20,1:28:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,discuss or you'd like to have elaborated,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.20,1:28:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you can just
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.20,1:28:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,bring it up. Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.04,1:28:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.38,1:28:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.69,1:29:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't talk much about that, so I'm glad
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.69,1:29:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you brought it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.36,1:29:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The question was, why do we
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.36,1:29:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,have to keep moving up and down in the field?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.36,1:29:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is something that
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.72,1:29:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we didn't discuss before, and I'm glad you
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.72,1:29:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of brought it up. That the energy
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.72,1:29:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,field comes about as a result of
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.72,1:29:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,one's commitment. In other words,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.72,1:29:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the power
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.72,1:29:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to create a certain energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.72,1:29:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,by my free will,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.72,1:29:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,by my agreement, by my assent,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.72,1:29:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,by the alignment of my goals,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.42,1:29:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,my purpose, my intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.42,1:29:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that sets the power of the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.87,1:29:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, within that,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.87,1:29:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,there may be daily variations
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.87,1:29:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,like the stock market. There is
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.87,1:29:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,jiggles up and down. So a person who is
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.87,1:29:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,committed to lovingness
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.87,1:29:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,may still experience these feelings.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.87,1:29:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And feelings, as you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.87,1:29:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,move very rapidly. Sometimes
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.87,1:29:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,change half a dozen times without
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.87,1:29:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,a second, those fleeting
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.87,1:29:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,fluctuations. So this is sort of
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.87,1:29:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,scintillating, changing. Those
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.87,1:29:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who see auras, especially auras
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.87,1:30:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,in color, see that scintillation
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.87,1:30:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of the constant shifting of the emotional fields.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.87,1:30:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But the person's commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.09,1:30:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,hasn't changed. Their commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.09,1:30:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.09,1:30:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the same person before and after
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.09,1:30:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience. The person
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.09,1:30:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,who changes their commitment, that is a different story.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.09,1:30:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But your commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.19,1:30:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is the same. So you can be committed
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.19,1:30:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to a loving relationship
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.19,1:30:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and suddenly get mad as the
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.19,1:30:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,devil at them. Suddenly angry
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.19,1:30:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,at them and that will flare up
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.19,1:30:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,from the solar plexus. But that
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.19,1:30:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't change your intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.19,1:30:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't change your commitment.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.19,1:30:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be mad at your boss. That doesn't mean you're quitting
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.19,1:30:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,today. It just means that you're angry at him today.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.19,1:30:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your commitment to do a good job
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.19,1:30:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and your commitment to work for this company or your
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.19,1:30:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,commitment to your career
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.19,1:30:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to remain the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.19,1:30:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Some days you may be enthusiastic about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.19,1:30:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Some days you may feel it's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.19,1:30:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never become a whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.19,1:30:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can fluctuate in the
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.05,1:30:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,scintillating emotionality
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.05,1:30:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but the commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.05,1:31:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,remains the same. The commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.05,1:31:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,remains the same and therefore your power
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.05,1:31:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the field of the commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.05,1:31:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's the commitment that holds the power.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.05,1:31:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.12,1:31:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that has set the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.12,1:31:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field, see let's
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.24,1:31:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,say one time at the
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.24,1:31:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,bill a girl said to me, after hearing your lecture she said
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.24,1:31:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I really feel bad about my
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.24,1:31:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,resentments now. And I said, well that's
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.24,1:31:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,easy to get rid of. You can get rid of
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.24,1:31:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that very easily. Just hate the son of a
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.24,1:31:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,bitch. I mean if you set this as
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.24,1:31:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,your goal then
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.24,1:31:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,resentments won't make you feel guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.24,1:31:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you set this as
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.11,1:31:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the goal then
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.11,1:31:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,so whatever level we set for ourself
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.11,1:31:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what becomes unacceptable
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.11,1:31:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to us is that which is below it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.11,1:31:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In a group where
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.43,1:31:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,angriness is okay
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.43,1:31:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,then you don't feel upset about resentments.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.43,1:31:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you move up to a commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.43,1:31:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to loving this, now resentments
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.43,1:31:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,become painful. And
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.43,1:31:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the desire is to be rid of that resentment
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.43,1:31:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.43,1:31:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people have utilized
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.68,1:32:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,this intuitively
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.68,1:32:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in grand
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.68,1:32:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,social demonstrations.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.68,1:32:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you want to remember how to utilize
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.68,1:32:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,these energy fields positively
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.68,1:32:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,just remember
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.68,1:32:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the social demonstration of the black
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.68,1:32:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,people in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.68,1:32:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In my lifetime I watched them move
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.68,1:32:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,from the bottom of the box all the way to the top.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.68,1:32:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was young
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.07,1:32:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,they all lived at the back of the bus. Black people
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.07,1:32:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,belonged at the back of the bus.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.07,1:32:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And they were into hopelessness and apathy.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.07,1:32:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And that hopelessness and apathy
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.07,1:32:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,was represented in the physical
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.07,1:32:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,attitude and the way they
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.07,1:32:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,walked and the way they shuffled
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.07,1:32:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in that hopeless apathy
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.07,1:32:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,because nothing was ever going to get better.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.07,1:32:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It became a caricature
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.07,1:32:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a stereotype on the stage
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.07,1:32:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of that walk
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.07,1:32:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of hopelessness and apathy
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.07,1:32:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and the grief over
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.07,1:32:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the grief over
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.10,1:32:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,how men express
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.10,1:32:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,primarily by the women
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.10,1:32:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,over the hopelessness of the situation
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.10,1:33:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,over the cost, over the realization
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.10,1:33:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that her children would never have a chance
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.10,1:33:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in this world. All of this
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.58,1:33:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,controlled by the tremendous fear
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.58,1:33:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the fear of the lynch mob. If the black man
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.58,1:33:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,protested he got hung from the
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.58,1:33:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,nearest tree. And so the intimidation
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.58,1:33:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and the terror, progressive
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.58,1:33:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,systematized terrorization.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.58,1:33:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then along came television
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.00,1:33:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and the submerged
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.00,1:33:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,part of the world, the third world
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.00,1:33:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the black people in America began
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.00,1:33:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to see, began to see
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.00,1:33:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,through television that which the rest
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.00,1:33:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world has. They began to see
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.00,1:33:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what other people have. The kind of houses
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.00,1:33:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,they lived in and the way they
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.00,1:33:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the style, the lifestyle, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.51,1:33:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of that desiringness
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.51,1:33:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and wantingness came anger and the frustration
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.51,1:33:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of that. And then we saw
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.51,1:33:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the arriving of black pride
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.51,1:33:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the pride in one's blackness
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.51,1:33:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,now. No longer the shame
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.51,1:33:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the self-effacement
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.51,1:33:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the fear about it
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.51,1:33:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,we saw the black anger and the
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.51,1:33:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,angerness. The energy
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.51,1:33:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the upside of that angerness
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.51,1:34:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,was then
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.54,1:34:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,through the intuition, through the inspiration
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.54,1:34:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of some of their great leaders
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.54,1:34:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,led into black pride. Out of the anger
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.54,1:34:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,then the energy of the anger
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.54,1:34:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is built into black pride.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.54,1:34:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There was some expression of the downside
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.54,1:34:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,some of the teenagers, the expression of the
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.54,1:34:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,angerness in the form of anger
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.54,1:34:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and destructiveness as
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.54,1:34:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,happened also in pride.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.64,1:34:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But a great, enough of that energy
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.64,1:34:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,was utilized in a positive way.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.64,1:34:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And so out of the pride you saw the courage
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.64,1:34:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to face and cope with
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.64,1:34:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what are the problems that have to be handled
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.64,1:34:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,here to change our way of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.64,1:34:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And there you saw
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.64,1:34:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the legal battles and you saw
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.64,1:34:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the bringing in
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.64,1:34:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of the courts and of social conscience
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.64,1:34:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the enlistment
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.64,1:34:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of the energy and the power
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.64,1:34:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of the white population
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.64,1:34:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as they become inspired to
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.64,1:34:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a higher view of man.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.64,1:34:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So we saw them move through courage
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.64,1:34:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,up through
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.64,1:34:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the acceptance of that which needs to be
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.64,1:34:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,handled and needs to be done
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.64,1:35:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the acceptance of equality on the part of
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.64,1:35:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,white people who had never even thought of it in their
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.64,1:35:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetime now began to think
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.64,1:35:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that perhaps black people are the same
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.64,1:35:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,equal to us and the emergence
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.64,1:35:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of love. And you saw the success
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.64,1:35:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of many social movements and of course
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.64,1:35:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the black people who were now once at the back of the bus
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.64,1:35:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in my lifetime are now mayors of cities
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.64,1:35:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and great entertainers and millionaires
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.64,1:35:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and leaders of industry
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.64,1:35:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and senators and congressmen
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.64,1:35:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the rest. So not all
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.64,1:35:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of their population but certainly a size
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.64,1:35:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of Lamont has demonstrated
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.64,1:35:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,how to utilize
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.64,1:35:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,these levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.64,1:35:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How to use the upside. How to use
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.64,1:35:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy of it. How to
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.64,1:35:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,utilize the energy of the anger and the
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.64,1:35:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,indignation to mobilize
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.64,1:35:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,social forces to bring
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.64,1:35:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,about changes in the senate, in the congress,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.64,1:35:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in the governors, in the
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.86,1:35:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,laws on the municipal
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.86,1:35:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,state federal level.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.86,1:35:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How to enlist the moral support
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.86,1:35:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of the country. You know
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.86,1:35:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,great power coming out of that
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.86,1:35:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,inspiration, that dedication
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.86,1:36:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to a cause that is greater than one's self.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.86,1:36:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The dedication to a cause
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.86,1:36:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that is greater than one's self
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.86,1:36:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,then allowed the power
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.86,1:36:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to express itself in that social
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.86,1:36:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,transition. In powerful
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.86,1:36:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,social changes. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.51,1:36:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a very good point.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.53,1:36:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That when you fall below
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.53,1:36:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you are committed to, what you run into
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.53,1:36:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is pain. And therefore it is
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.53,1:36:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,self-educating. You know that
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.53,1:36:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it's out because it doesn't feel right anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.53,1:36:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,See when you're dedicated
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.53,1:36:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to hating this, you're dedicated to
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.53,1:36:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,hating this, everything below it is
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.53,1:36:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,painful. When you're dedicated to
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.53,1:36:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,pride let's say.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.53,1:36:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're dedicated to pride then fear
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.53,1:36:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is no longer acceptable. And that's
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.53,1:36:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,part of the passages of the adolescent
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.53,1:36:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,boy. It's part of the passages
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.53,1:37:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of becoming
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.53,1:37:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the United States Marine Corps let's say.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.53,1:37:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The expression
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.53,1:37:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,or the overt acknowledgement
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.53,1:37:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of this is no longer acceptable
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.53,1:37:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because now what you're committed to
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.53,1:37:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is pride. They'll say brace up boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.53,1:37:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Brace up boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.53,1:37:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are only bullets.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.53,1:37:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll tear your guts to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.53,1:37:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are only bullets.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.53,1:37:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean they'll only go through you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.53,1:37:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's to be afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.53,1:37:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And so
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.53,1:37:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and then when I was in the Navy I was on a
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.53,1:37:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,minesweeper and of course we swept
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.53,1:37:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,mines in the East China Sea so
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.53,1:37:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,minesweepers were blowing up all over
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.53,1:37:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so it wasn't you were going to get bullets
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.53,1:37:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you were going to just get blown up.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.53,1:37:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So we all went into neutral.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.53,1:37:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We all went into
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.53,1:37:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,if you blow up you blow up and if you don't
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.63,1:37:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.63,1:37:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When we went out to sweep mines you
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.63,1:37:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,battened all the hatches and you had to take your
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.63,1:37:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,stuff, whatever stuff you needed for the day
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.63,1:37:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,from below you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.63,1:37:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they battened the hatches nobody was allowed to be
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.63,1:37:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,below hatches because if you blew up
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.63,1:38:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the compression there would like, I don't want you to go
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.63,1:38:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,into an anatomical description but
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.63,1:38:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you stayed above decks.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.08,1:38:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was the way it was handled.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.08,1:38:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was handled in
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.33,1:38:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so fatalism we might add that as a
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.33,1:38:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,neat way of neutral.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.33,1:38:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The fatalist then is a good expression
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.33,1:38:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of that energy field.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.33,1:38:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you blow up you blow up and if you don't you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.33,1:38:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know what difference does it make?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.33,1:38:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean when you go
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.33,1:38:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's the fatalistic
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.33,1:38:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and many men in our
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.33,1:38:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,society have developed that
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.33,1:38:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you know as a result of their experiences in the war
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.33,1:38:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it was really the only way you could handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.33,1:38:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you can't walk around in a panic all day long
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.33,1:38:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's socially unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.33,1:38:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be angry about.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.33,1:38:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be into apathy
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.56,1:38:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.56,1:38:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And lovingness just doesn't seem
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.56,1:38:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the lovingness is the
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.56,1:38:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,bonding that goes on between the men
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.56,1:38:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and so there are those profound
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.56,1:38:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,bonds of love which last
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.56,1:38:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,many years. This last year I
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.56,1:38:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,happened to get together with a friend I hadn't
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.56,1:38:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,seen in 40 years who was
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.56,1:39:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,with me in the navy back in
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.56,1:39:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,1945.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.56,1:39:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But 40 years later that
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.56,1:39:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,commitment, that bonding of love
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.56,1:39:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,had not changed when I
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.56,1:39:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,saw him or loved him just as much
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.56,1:39:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,as I always had as though 40 years had
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.56,1:39:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,never gone by. So that
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.78,1:39:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,bonding and that love. So that was the strength
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.78,1:39:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,then, the strength
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.78,1:39:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which that strength is coming
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.78,1:39:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle the threat to life
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.78,1:39:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,itself on its most dramatic
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.78,1:39:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,expression from moment to moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.78,1:39:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So all these things have their
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.78,1:39:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,positive
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.84,1:39:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,way of holding them positively.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.84,1:39:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly better to be detached
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.84,1:39:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly better to be into fatalism
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.84,1:39:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,than to be in a state of panic
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.84,1:39:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,which is paralyzing you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.84,1:39:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in neutrality we can function
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.84,1:39:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and we all do.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.77,1:39:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.77,1:39:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and knowing that it's there
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.19,1:39:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's attainable
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.19,1:40:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet having setbacks
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.89,1:40:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and conscious
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.52,1:40:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness and working of
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.52,1:40:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,within my mind
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.52,1:40:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the things I need to do to come back
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.52,1:40:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to that higher level.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.52,1:40:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire to return to that
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.02,1:40:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,level. What? What? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.02,1:40:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Am I
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.05,1:40:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,a creature of nature and
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.05,1:40:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I go back there automatically?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.05,1:40:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I use my left brain to bring myself
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.05,1:40:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,back there? Can I apply
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.40,1:40:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,logic to
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.40,1:40:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the attainment of ecstasy?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.40,1:40:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What we've been talking about today is
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.32,1:40:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is a balance between
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.32,1:40:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,left and right brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.76,1:40:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Being, having grown up as a left
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.76,1:40:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,brain person, then having become
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.76,1:40:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,excessively a right brain person
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.76,1:40:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and then coming back to balance.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.76,1:40:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What we try to do is
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.76,1:40:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,express all of this in a balanced way
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.76,1:40:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because the left brain
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.76,1:40:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so often will take
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.76,1:41:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the position that the right
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.76,1:41:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,brain way of viewing things
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.76,1:41:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is illogical.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.76,1:41:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And so by the research we've been
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.76,1:41:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,doing you see that
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.76,1:41:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth is approachable equally from
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.76,1:41:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,either left or right brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.76,1:41:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the left brain
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.76,1:41:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,begins all of this, it now no longer
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.76,1:41:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,has any objection. It is logical,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.76,1:41:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's scientifically
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.76,1:41:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,demonstrable, but
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.92,1:41:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,they're generally, you can test them with
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.92,1:41:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,kinesiology, you can get the same,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.92,1:41:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you can test each other with kinesiology, you can just say
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.92,1:41:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, if I hold in mind pride
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.92,1:41:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is it over 150, or 160, or
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.92,1:41:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,170, or 170, about 175 a Sunday
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.92,1:41:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a week? It is not above 175.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.92,1:41:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can set these and verify
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.92,1:41:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,them experientially, the truth of this
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.92,1:41:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,within yourself. That removes
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.92,1:41:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the objections of the left brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.92,1:41:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To the fact that this is not logical.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.92,1:41:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.92,1:41:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody was a more skeptical left brain person
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.92,1:41:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,than myself. I didn't believe
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.92,1:41:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,any of this. You see the mystic
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.49,1:41:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,is not, the wisdom of the mystic
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.49,1:42:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,is not accessible to the left brain
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.49,1:42:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,person. Because the mystic
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.74,1:42:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences it, but he can't
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.74,1:42:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,communicate it to a left brain person
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.74,1:42:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in any way that's useful to the left brain person.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.74,1:42:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.89,1:42:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,what we tried to do is translate
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.89,1:42:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it into language.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.89,1:42:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the truth is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.89,1:42:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If the truth is true, then it's true on all levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.89,1:42:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And it should be as understandable from
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.89,1:42:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,one side as the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.32,1:42:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Death being zero, that's rather obvious, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.32,1:42:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.32,1:42:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you start with the proposition
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.32,1:42:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that death is zero,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.32,1:42:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can use like kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.32,1:42:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that we use today. You can say if death is zero
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.32,1:42:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,then what is the relative energy fueled
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.32,1:42:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of apathy?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.32,1:42:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can calibrate this for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.32,1:42:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is the relative energy fueled
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.32,1:42:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of desire? Then what is the relative
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.32,1:42:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,energy fueled of anger? It's very simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.32,1:42:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, I'm holding anger
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.32,1:43:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in mind. Is that over 70?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.32,1:43:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that over 80? Is that over 90?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.32,1:43:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that over 100? Is that over 120?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.32,1:43:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that over 140? Is that over 150?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.32,1:43:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And at 150 your body will say
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.32,1:43:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that's its relative strength
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.32,1:43:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,as compared.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.32,1:43:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you keep doing that all the way up,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.32,1:43:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll end up with the same numbers that I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.32,1:43:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we've verified this
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.32,1:43:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,with a number of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.35,1:43:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you use those energy fuels, those are about the kind of
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.35,1:43:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,numbers that you will come up with.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.35,1:43:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the value of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.35,1:43:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The value of it is mind-boggling.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.35,1:43:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,For those who can see,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.35,1:43:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it is mind-boggling, the implications
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.35,1:43:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of these numbers
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.35,1:43:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and the reversities of these
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.35,1:43:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,energy fuels.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.35,1:43:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives you a way to hold
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.35,1:43:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,all of human experience now
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.35,1:43:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,from a way that becomes self-healing
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.35,1:43:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,through that understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.35,1:43:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the whole purpose of today's
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.35,1:43:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.35,1:43:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The talk is really about self-healing
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.35,1:43:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course self-healing
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.35,1:43:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,explicitly as it applies to the
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.35,1:43:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,addictions, but we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.35,1:44:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the basic principles
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.35,1:44:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of self-healing in general.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.35,1:44:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What we say today really applies
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.35,1:44:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to everyone and
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.35,1:44:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of course we related it specifically
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.35,1:44:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to the addictions.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.35,1:44:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What we're talking about is the nature of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.35,1:44:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,itself, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.35,1:44:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,aside from the addictions,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.35,1:44:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but with its special
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.44,1:44:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,application to the
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.44,1:44:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,addictions themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.92,1:44:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you'd be willing to give up
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.88,1:44:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,if really asked for all?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.88,1:44:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For what would you give up
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.07,1:44:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,all of it? For what would you say
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.58,1:44:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,take it?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.80,1:44:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you willing to die for? What are you willing
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.66,1:44:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to commit to?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.92,1:44:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the limitations
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.98,1:44:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and the considerations?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.96,1:44:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When people get sober, we ask them to make
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.96,1:44:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the same commitment as
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.12,1:44:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they did before.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.44,1:44:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the fifth chapter
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.44,1:44:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in the book Alcoholics Anonymous, it says
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.44,1:45:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that those
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.44,1:45:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,who succeeded in getting sober
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.31,1:45:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,were those who did not
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.31,1:45:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,draw any line in how far they were willing to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.31,1:45:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever was needed,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.31,1:45:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,they were willing to go the whole way
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.31,1:45:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for whatever was needed.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.76,1:45:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That they did not hold back.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.76,1:45:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That sobriety came only to those who were willing
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.76,1:45:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to go the whole way.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.17,1:45:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever was asked, the willingness to go
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.17,1:45:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole route. And it was out of that
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.17,1:45:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that sobriety arose.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.17,1:45:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to go the whole way.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.17,1:45:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To hold back nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.17,1:45:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if life itself is asked.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.17,1:45:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With that spiritual awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.74,1:45:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,then, there comes
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.74,1:45:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,an unlimitedness to what one is
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.74,1:45:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,willing to let go of
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.74,1:45:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of that
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.87,1:45:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,intention, in the name of that goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.87,1:45:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.19,1:45:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.84,1:45:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,here's Leo. Thanks Leo
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.12,1:45:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for this opportunity to be here today.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.12,1:46:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we would like to thank
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.48,1:46:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dave Hawkins. I'd like to give a hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.48,1:46:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps a few of you would
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.27,1:46:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,want to say a few words of thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.27,1:46:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't here for the whole day
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.27,1:46:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can't really comment. I know
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.27,1:46:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the parts that I heard I was very much
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.27,1:46:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,impressed with and very much
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.27,1:46:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightened and moved by.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.27,1:46:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Would anyone want to
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.27,1:46:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,say a few words
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.27,1:46:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of what they got out of today or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.27,1:46:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.23,1:46:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like hearing it
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.23,1:46:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,explained to me. Somehow giving it some
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.42,1:46:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.42,1:46:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just been grateful all day that you do this for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.42,1:46:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I forgot
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.48,1:46:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to say today, and I usually do, that
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.48,1:46:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't hear anything today that you don't
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.48,1:46:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,already know. You're just not
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.48,1:46:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,conscious that you know it. And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.48,1:46:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's an intense feeling of familiarity.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.48,1:46:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As we talk about this, it's like
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.48,1:47:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I always knew that. Part of me
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.48,1:47:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,always knew this, and that part
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.48,1:47:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of me that always knew it, but
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.48,1:47:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,forgot it, brought me here today
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.48,1:47:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to remind itself
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.48,1:47:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is useful
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.48,1:47:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in that knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.57,1:47:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple exercise.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.98,1:47:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.20,1:47:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of my joy. The reason I
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.20,1:47:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,give these talks here or any place
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.49,1:47:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,else is the sheer joy I get
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.49,1:47:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,out of doing it, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.49,1:47:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The sheer joy
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.72,1:47:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,out of just sharing it. That
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.72,1:47:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,which I experience benefit
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.75,1:47:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,from myself. And
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.00,1:47:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the joy of sharing that
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.00,1:47:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with other people. That's the great
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.00,1:47:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,joy of it. I appreciate how you gave our
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.69,1:47:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,left brain something to focus on while
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.69,1:47:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you were creating this whole context and energy
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.69,1:47:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,field with your energy
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.69,1:47:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,field and really inducting us into all the
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.69,1:48:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,information. Great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.69,1:48:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels terrific.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.69,1:48:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. All of it happened
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.01,1:48:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,as it was, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.72,1:48:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine. Thank you very much, Dave. We are truly grateful.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.72,1:48:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again, Bill.
